re%20okay%20to%20ignore%20the%20simmering%20civil%20war%20in%20Manipur%3B%20the%20constant%20stream%20of%20deaths%20does%20not%20disturb%20us.%20We%20are%20okay%20to%20ignore%20that%20our%20education%20system%20lies%20in%20tatters.%20We%20are%20okay%20with%20the%20tyranny%20that%20we%20inflict%20on%20Kashmir%2C%20which%20the%20pusillanimous%20Supreme%20Court%20justifies%20under%20the%20furtherance%20of%20a%20supposedly%20democratic%20constitution.%20We%20are%20okay%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20our%20foreign%20policy%20is%20so%20full%20of%20bombast%20and%20boasts%20that%20we%20have%20become%20a%20joke%20within%20our%20own%20region%2C%20much%20less%20further%20abroad.%20We%20are%20okay%20to%20lie%20about%20our%20female%20labour%20force%20participation%20when%20the%20world%20knows%20that%20we%20are%20the%20laggards%20of%20the%20region%2C%20competing%20only%20with%20Pakistan%20and%20Afghanistan%20for%20the%20bottom%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERuled%20by%20liars%20and%20cowards%2C%20India%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20being%20a%20country%20where%20we%20go%20to%20bed%20praying%20that%20our%20government%20does%20not%20embarrass%20us%20further%2C%20and%20yet%2C%20inevitably%2C%20it%20does.%20Being%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20stories%20of%20Rama%20have%20been%20with%20me%20throughout%20my%20life.%20After%20all%2C%20it%20is%20in%20the%20forests%20of%20Poorvanchal%20that%20his%20sons%2C%20Luv%20and%20Kush%2C%20are%20supposed%20to%20have%20confronted%20the%20godking.%20One%20of%20the%20central%20themes%20of%20the%20Ramayana%20is%20Rama%E2%80%99s%20willingness%20to%20forego%20his%20crown%20due%20to%20the%20scheming%20of%20his%20stepmother%20and%20the%20thoughtless%20promise%20of%20his%20father.%20When%20his%20stepmother%20compels%20him%20to%20go%20into%20exile%20so%20that%20her%20son%2C%20Bharata%2C%20can%20rule%20in%20his%20stead%2C%20Rama%20honours%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20promise%20made%20in%20a%20time%20of%20weakness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20when%20Bharata%20pl