-to-play-t20-world-cup-former-cricketers-suggestion-to-star-batter%2Farticleshow%2F107079458.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Briefcase%20To%20'Bahi%20Khata'%3A%20How%20Budget%20Presentation%20Changed%20Over%20The%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFor%20decades%2C%20finance%20ministers%20have%20been%20photographed%20carrying%20a%20briefcase%20into%20Parliament%20for%20the%20presentation%20of%20the%20Union%20Budget.%20The%20year%202019%20marked%20a%20big%20shift%20when%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20ditched%20this%20practice%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtvprofit.com%2Fbusiness%2Funion-budget-2022-briefcase-to-bahi-khata-to-tablet-a-look-at-the-journey-of-budget-presentation-2712127%5C%22%3E'bahi%20khata'%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20then%20opted%20for%20a%20paperless%20format%20in%202021%20by%20using%20a%20'Made%20in%20India'%20tablet.%20The%20journey%20of%20the%20presentation%20of%20the%20Union%20Budget%20from%20briefcase%20to%20a%20completely%20paperless%20mode%20is%20quite%20fascinating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFinance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20is%20all%20set%20to%20present%20the%20Interim%20Budget%20for%20FY%202024-25%20on%20February%201.%20A%20full-fledged%20Budget%20will%20be%20presented%20after%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20new%20government%20following%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%202019%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%2C%20while%20holding%20the%20additional%20charge%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%2C%20presented%20the%20last%20interim%20Budget.%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20presented%20her%20maiden%20Budget%20on%20July%205%2C%202019%2C%20after%20assuming%20charge%20as%20the%20finance%20minister%20following%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20government's%20second%20consecutive%20win%20in%20the%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAhead%20of%20the%20Budget%202024%2C%20let's%20take%20a%20look%20at%20the%20history%20behind%20the%20Union%20Budget%20presentation%20exercise%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBriefcase%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERK%20Shanmukham%20Chetty%2C%20the%20first%20Finance%20Minister%20of%20independent%20India%2C%20continued%20with%20the%20British-era%20tradition%20by%20carrying%20the%20documents%20related%20to%20the%20first%20Union%20Budget%20in%20a%20leather%20portfolio%20bag.%20This%20tradition%20continued%20for%20the%20next%20few%20years%20as%20the%20finance%20ministers%20used%20different%20briefcases%20for%20the%20Budget%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWith%20time%2C%20this%20practice%20evolved%20as%20per%20the%20needs.%20In%20the%201970s%2C%20finance%20ministers%20had%20started%20carrying%20a%20hardbound%20bag%20%E2%80%93%20the%20colour%20of%20which%20continued%20to%20change%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20'budget%20briefcase'%20was%20a%20remnant%20of%20the%20colonial%20era%20and%20similar%20to%20the%20Gladstone%20Box%2C%20named%20after%20the%20former%20British%20Chancellor%20of%20the%20Exchequer%2C%20William%20Ewart%20Gladstone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Bahi%20Khata'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20old%20'budget%20briefcase'%20was%20replaced%20with%20the%20'bahi%20khata'%20soon%20after%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20government%20secured%20a%20second%20consecutive%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDuring%20her%20first%20Budget%2C%20Finance%20Minister%20Sitharaman%20drew%20the%20nation's%20attention%20by%20carrying%20a%20red-coloured%20%E2%80%98bahi%20khata'%20in%202019%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20briefcase.%20The%20reason%20behind%20this%20appeared%20to%20be%20the%20renunciation%20of%20the%20colonial%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHer%20decision%20to%20use%20the%20'bahi%20khata'%20gave%20an%20Indian%20touch%20to%20the%20budgetary%20exercise%20as%20it%20has%20been%20used%20by%20business%20owners%20for%20decades%20to%20maintain%20their%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBack%20then%2C%20FM%20Sitharaman%20said%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Beasier%26quot%3B%20to%20carry%20the%20'bahi%20khata'%20and%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20Indian%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETablet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20traditional%20'bahi%20khata'%20gave%20way%20to%20a%20more%20modern%20device%20as%20FM%20Sitharaman%20presented%20the%20Budget%20in%20a%20paperless%20format%2C%20using%20a%20'Made%20in%20India'%20tablet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20move%20was%20also%20in%20tandem%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20push%20for%20a%20'Digital%20India'.%20This%20was%20also%20the%20first%20Budget%20presentation%20since%20the%20outbreak%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMs%20Sitharaman%20carried%20the%20tablet%20in%20a%20red%20'bahi%20khata'-style%20pouch%20in%202021%20and%20continued%20this%20practice%20in%202022%20and%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20year%20too%2C%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20is%20expected%20to%20present%20Budget%202024%20in%20paperless%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706001240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2F1aqpatho_budget-2023-bahi-khata_625x300_17_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbriefcase-to-bahi-khata-how-budget-presentation-changed-over-the-years-4915899%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20decades%2C%20finance%20ministers%20have%20been%20photographed%20carrying%20a%20briefcase%20into%20Parliament%20for%20the%20presentation%20of%20the%20Union%20Budget.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.