in%20his%20relevance%20room...%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ayodhya's%20New%20Ram%20Lalla%20Idol%20To%20Be%20Known%20As%20'Balak%20Ram'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20Ram%20Lalla%20idol%20consecrated%20at%20the%20grand%20Ram%20temple%20on%20Monday%20will%20be%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BBalak%20Ram%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20depicts%20the%20deity%20as%20a%20five-year-old%20boy%20in%20a%20standing%20posture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idol%20of%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20whose%20consecration%20was%20done%20on%20January%2022%2C%20has%20been%20named%20as%20'Balak%20Ram'.%20The%20reason%20for%20naming%20the%20idol%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20as%20'Balak%20Ram'%20is%20that%20he%20resembles%20a%20child%2C%20whose%20age%20is%20five%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Arun%20Dixit%2C%20a%20priest%20associated%20with%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20time%20I%20saw%20the%20idol%2C%20I%20was%20thrilled%20and%20tears%20started%20rolling%20down%20my%20face.%20I%20cannot%20explain%20the%20feeling%20I%20experienced%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Varanasi-based%20priest%2C%20who%20has%20conducted%20nearly%2050-60%20consecrations%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOf%20all%20the%20consecrations%20(I%20have)%20performed%20so%20far%2C%20this%20is%20the%20most%20'alaukik%20(divine)'%20and%20'sarvoch'%20(supreme)%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%20Dixit%20said%20he%20had%20the%20first%20glimpse%20of%20the%20idol%20on%20January%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idol%20was%20consecrated%20on%20Monday%20in%20a%20grand%20ceremony%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20said%20it%20marked%20the%20advent%20of%20a%20new%20era.%20The%20old%20idol%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%2C%20which%20was%20earlier%20kept%20in%20a%20makeshift%20shrine%2C%20has%20been%20placed%20in%20front%20of%20the%20new%20idol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakhs%20of%20people%20watched%20the%20'pran%20pratishtha%20(consecration)'%20ceremony%20on%20television%20in%20their%20homes%20and%20neighbourhood%20temples%2C%20becoming%20part%20of%20the%20historic%20event%20held%20just%20months%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%2C%20the%20ornaments%20for%20the%20idol%20have%20been%20prepared%20after%20extensive%20research%20and%20study%20of%20texts%20such%20as%20the%20Adhyatma%20Ramayana%2C%20Valmiki%20Ramayana%2C%20Ramcharitmanas%20and%20the%20Alavandar%20Stotram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idol%20is%20adorned%20in%20Banarasi%20fabric%2C%20featuring%20a%20yellow%20dhoti%20and%20a%20red%20'pataka'%20or%20'angavastram'.%20The%20'angavastram'%20are%20embellished%20in%20pure%20gold%20'zari'%20and%20threads%2C%20featuring%20auspicious%20Vaishnav%20symbols%20--%20'shankh'%2C%20'padma'%2C%20'chakra'%20and%20'mayur'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20ornaments%20have%20been%20crafted%20by%20Ankur%20Anand's%20Lucknow-based%20Harsahaimal%20Shiamlal%20Jewellers%2C%20the%20garments%20were%20created%20by%20Delhi-based%20textile%20designer%20Manish%20Tripathi%2C%20who%20worked%20from%20Ayodhya%20Dham%20for%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2051-inch%20idol%20chiselled%20by%20Mysuru-based%20sculptor%20Arun%20Yogiraj%20has%20been%20carved%20out%20of%20a%20three%20billion-year-old%20rock.%20The%20azure-coloured%20Krishna%20Shile%20(black%20schist)%20was%20excavated%20from%20Gujjegowdanapura%20at%20Jayapura%20Hobli%20in%20HD%20Kote%20Taluk%20of%20Mysuru.%20It%20is%20a%20fine-to-medium-grained%2C%20sky-blue%20metamorphic%20rock%2C%20generally%20called%20soapstone%20because%20of%20its%20smooth%20surface%20texture%20and%20is%20ideal%20for%20sculptors%20to%20carve%20idols.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Krishna%20Shile%20was%20found%20while%20levelling%20the%20agricultural%20land%20of%20Ramdas%20(78)%20and%20a%20local%20contractor%2C%20who%20assessed%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20stone%2C%20drew%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20temple%20trustees%20in%20Ayodhya%20through%20his%20contacts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYogiraj%2C%20who%20has%20received%20effusive%20praise%20for%20his%20work%2C%20told%20PTI%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20always%20felt%20that%20Lord%20Ram%20has%20been%20shielding%20me%20and%20my%20family%20from%20all%20the%20bad%20times%20and%20I%20strongly%20believe%20that%20it%20was%20Him%20who%20chose%20me%20for%20the%20auspicious%20task.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BI%20spent%20sleepless%20nights%20working%20on%20the%20idol%20with%20precision%20but%20it%20was%20all%20worth%20it.%20I%20feel%20I%20am%20the%20luckiest%20person%20on%20Earth%20and%20today%20is%20the%20best%20day%20of%20my%20life.%20I%20learnt%20the%20art%20of%20sculpting%20from%20my%20father.%20He%20would%20have%20been%20very%20proud%20to%20see%20my%20idol%20here%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERama%20Lalla%20idols%20for%20the%20grand%20temple%20were%20made%20by%20three%20sculptors%20--%20Ganesh%20Bhatt%2C%20Yogiraj%20and%20Satyanarayan%20Pandey.%20The%20temple%20trust%20said%20that%20of%20the%20three%2C%20one%20would%20be%20placed%20in%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20while%20the%20other%20two%20kept%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20mandir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706000880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F86t64ve8_ram-lalla-idol_625x300_23_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhyas-new-ram-lalla-idol-to-be-known-as-balak-ram-4916322%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20new%20Ram%20Lalla%20idol%20consecrated%20at%20the%20grand%20Ram%20temple%20on%20Monday%20will%20be%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BBalak%20Ram%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20depicts%20the%20deity%20as%20a%20five-year-old%20boy%20in%20a%20standing%20posture.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhyas-new-ram-lalla-idol-to-be-known-as-balak-ram-4916322%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhyas-new-ram-lalla-idol-to-be-known-as-balak-ram-4916322%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhyas-new-ram-lalla-idol-to-be-known-as-balak-ram-4916322%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Massive%20Data%20Leak%20Of%2026%20Billion%20Records%20Detected%3A%20%26quot%3BMother%20Of%20All%20Breaches%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESecurity%20researchers%20have%20revealed%20that%20a%20massive%20database%20containing%20no%20less%20than%2026%20billion%20leaked%20records%20has%20been%20discovered%20on%20an%20unsecured%20page.%20Dubbed%20%26quot%3BMother%20of%20all%20Breaches%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20the%20biggest%20found%20till%20date%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20database%20contains%20sensitive%20information%20from%20several%20sites%20including%20Twitter%2C%20Dropbox%20and%20LinkedIn.%20The%20breach%20was%20discovered%20by%20researchers%20from%20Security%20Discovery%20and%20Cybernews%20and%20runs%20to%2012%20terabytes%20in%20size%2C%20%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E%20further%20said%20in%20its%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20team%20believes%20the%20database%20was%20compiled%20by%20a%20malicious%20actor%20or%20data%20broker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThreat%20actors%20could%20leverage%20the%20aggregated%20data%20for%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20attacks%2C%20including%20identity%20theft%2C%20sophisticated%20phishing%20schemes%2C%20targeted%20cyberattacks%2C%20and%20unauthorized%20access%20to%20personal%20and%20sensitive%20accounts%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcybernews.com%2Fsecurity%2Fbillions-passwords-credentials-leaked-mother-of-all-breaches%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20researchers%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leaked%20data%20also%20has%20records%20of%20users%20from%20Chinese%20messaging%20giant%20Tencent%20and%20social%20media%20platform%20Weibo.%20Records%20from%20Adobe%2C%20Canva%20and%20Telegram%20have%20also%20been%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorryingly%2C%20the%20researchers%20said%20that%20records%20from%20an%20assortment%20of%20US%20and%20other%20government%20organizations%20can%20be%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20good%20news%20is%20that%20only%20a%20minor%20part%20of%20the%20database%20is%20new.%20The%20researchers%20said%20that%20it's%20more%20a%20case%20of%20compiled%20records%20from%20thousands%20of%20previous%20breaches%20and%20data%20leaks%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fdaveywinder%2F2024%2F01%2F22%2Fmassive-26-billion-record-leak-dropbox-linkedin-twitterx-all-named%2F%3Fsh%3D74a8f7f7472a%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20concerning%20part%20is%20that%20it%20includes%20several%20username%20and%20password%20combinations.%20Cyber%20criminals%20can%20make%20use%20of%20this%20data%20to%20carry%20out%20attacks%20such%20as%20identity%20theft%2C%20sophisticated%20phishing%20schemes%2C%20targeted%20cyberattacks%2C%20and%20gain%20unauthorised%20access%20to%20personal%20and%20sensitive%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20should%20never%20underestimate%20what%20cybercriminals%20can%20achieve%20with%20such%20limited%20information.%20Victims%20need%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20consequences%20of%20stolen%20passwords%20and%20make%20the%20necessary%20security%20updates%20in%20response%2C%26quot%3B%20Jake%20Moore%2C%20global%20cybersecurity%20advisor%20at%20ESET%2C%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20nearly%20one%20billion%20records%20were%20leaked%20from%20an%20unsecured%20database%20created%20by%20Verifications.io.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20and%20most%20damaging%20leaks%20ever.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20other%20biggest%20leaks%20came%20from%20MySpace%20(360%20million)%2C%20Twitter%20(281%20million)%2C%20LinkedIn%20(251%20million)%20and%20AdultFriendFinder%20(220%20million).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706000640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2015-06%2Fcybercrime_650x400_71433937885.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmassive-data-leak-of-26-billion-records-from-sites-like-twitter-linkedin-detected-4915898%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20leaked%20data%20also%20has%20records%20of%20users%20from%20Chinese%20messaging%20giant%20Tencent%20and%20social%20media%20platform%20Weibo.%20Records%20from%20Adobe%2C%20Canva%20and%20Telegram%20have%20also%20been%20found.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmassive-data-leak-of-26-billion-records-from-sites-like-twitter-linkedin-detected-4915898%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmassive-data-leak-of-26-billion-records-from-sites-like-twitter-linkedin-detected-4915898%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmassive-data-leak-of-26-billion-records-from-sites-like-twitter-linkedin-detected-4915898%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gujarat%20Lifts%20Its%20Alcohol%20Ban%20for%20Some%3A%20A%20Sign%20of%20What%20Lies%20Ahead%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19170544%2Fimage-1075-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ESociologist%20M.N.%20Srinivas%20has%20written%20that%20the%20use%20of%20alcohol%20and%20intoxicants%20in%20Hindu%20religious%20rituals%20is%20part%20of%20the%20practices%20of%20popular%20and%20indigenous%20cultures.%20However%2C%20formal%20religious%20rites%20involve%20no%20alcohol%20and%2C%20like%20beef%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20consuming%20the%20%E2%80%9Csom%E2%80%9D%20intoxicant%20in%20a%20ritual%20was%20given%20up%20long%20ago%20and%20made%20taboo.%20In%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%2C%20the%20claim%20was%20made%20(by%20Congressman%20B.G.%20Kher)%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20drinking%20of%20liquor%20is%20one%20of%20the%20five%20deadly%20sins%20which%20the%20Smritis%20have%20laid%20down%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20that%20not%20only%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%2C%20but%20even%20Christians%20viewed%20it%20as%20a%20sin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20writing%20this%20from%20Gujarat%2C%20where%20the%20state%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fgujarat-lifts-liquor-ban-in-gift-city-netizens-say-dont-have-to-go-to-daman-and-diu-anymore-11703323574301.html%5C%22%3Ehas%20decided%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20lift%20prohibition%20in%20one%20part%20of%20the%20state.%20As%20a%20news%20report%20put%20it%2C%20this%20was%20done%20to%20%E2%80%9Cattract%20global%20financial%20institutions%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20to%20that%20end%20%E2%80%9Calcohol%20would%20be%20allowed%20at%20hotels%2Frestaurants%2Fclubs%20offering%20%E2%80%98wine%20and%20dine%E2%80%99%20in%20Gujarat%20International%20Finance%20Tec-City%20(or%20GIFT%20City)%20near%20the%20state%20capital%20of%20Gandhinagar.%E2%80%99%20This%2C%20the%20report%20added%2C%20would%20be%20available%20only%20to%20officials%2C%20employees%20and%20owners%20working%20from%20GIFT%20City%2C%20who%20would%20be%20exempt%20from%20the%20prohibition%20law%2C%20that%20makes%20the%20consumption%20of%20alcohol%20illegal%20across%20the%20state.%20Other%20Gujaratis%20who%20drank%20would%20continue%20to%20be%20forced%20to%20abstain%20or%20forced%20to%20do%20it%20illegally.%20It%20is%20quite%20interesting%20to%20see%20what%20the%20origin%20of%20the%20prohibition%20in%20law%20in%20India%20has%20been%2C%20from%20the%20constitutional%20point%20of%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20point%20was%20made%20by%20other%20members%20that%20alcohol%20was%20a%20part%20of%20Adivasi%20culture%20and%20ritual%2C%20Congressman%20V.I.%20Muniswami%20Pillai%20claimed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20is%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20require%20liquor%2C%20toddy%2C%20brandy%20or%20any%20such%20thing%2C%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20ceremonies%20of%20the%20aborigines%E2%80%9D.%20He%20said%20that%20alcohol%20came%20to%20the%20indigenous%20people%20with%20the%20British%20and%20had%20left%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spirited%20response%20to%20Hindu%20conservatives%20came%20from%20B.H.%20Khardekar%2C%20an%20Independent%2C%20who%20represented%20Kolhapur.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20arguments%20being%20put%20forward%20in%20favour%20of%20prohibition%20did%20not%20hold.%20The%20first%20argument%2C%20that%20the%20Americans%20had%20enforced%20it%20between%201920%20and%201933%2C%20was%20flawed%20because%20the%20Americans%20had%20let%20it%20go.%20The%20second%2C%20that%20the%20Congress%20Party%20had%20pledged%20itself%20to%20it%2C%20did%20not%20matter%20as%20the%20Congress%20was%20only%20one%20political%20party%20after%20Independence%20and%20did%20not%20represent%20the%20nation.%20The%20third%2C%20which%20was%20the%20claim%20that%20Parsis%20and%20Christians%20were%20also%20in%20favour%20of%20prohibition%2C%20was%20bogus.%20And%20last%2C%20that%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20was%20in%20favour%20of%20it%2C%20did%20not%20hold%20because%20Gandhi%20was%20also%20against%20compulsion%20of%20any%20kind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhardekar%20also%20spoke%20of%20lost%20excise%20revenues%20which%20could%20be%20put%20to%20use%20to%20build%20the%20state%20and%20also%20quoted%20the%20economist%20Harold%20Laski%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3ELiberty%20in%20the%20Modern%20State%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20which%20he%20says%20prohibition%20infringes%20on%20personal%20liberty.%20His%20is%20the%20most%20structured%20and%20factual%20intervention%20in%20the%20debate.%20But%20his%20primary%20arguments%20were%20dismissed%20by%20the%20others%20as%20being%20either%20of%20no%20consequence%20or%20resoluble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20absence%20of%20any%20pushback%20other%20than%20from%20Khardekar%2C%20and%20a%20clear%20Congress%20desire%20to%20push%20this%20through%20on%20moral%20grounds%2C%20the%20amendment%20was%20accepted.%20Article%2047%20reads%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20State%20shall%20regard%20the%20raising%20of%20the%20level%20of%20nutrition%20and%20the%20standard%20of%20living%20of%20its%20people%20and%20the%20improvement%20of%20public%20health%20as%20among%20its%20primary%20duties%20and%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20the%20State%20shall%20endeavour%20to%20bring%20about%20prohibition%20of%20the%20consumption%2C%20except%20for%20medicinal%20purposes%2C%20of%20intoxicating%20drinks%20and%20of%20drugs%20which%20are%20injurious%20to%20health.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20provision%20was%20smuggled%20in%20under%20the%20cloak%20of%20health%20and%20well-being.%20But%20as%20the%20decades%20have%20shown%2C%20the%20obligation%20of%20the%20State%20in%20the%20first%20part%2C%20of%20raising%20the%20levels%20of%20nutrition%20and%20standard%20of%20living%20and%20the%20improvement%20of%20health%2C%20and%20indeed%20these%20being%20its%20primary%20duties%2C%20has%20been%20followed%20in%20the%20breach.%20India%20stood%20129th%20out%20of%20189%20nations%20in%20the%202019%20United%20Nations%20Development%20Programme%E2%80%99s%20Human%20Development%20Index%2C%20which%20measures%20life%20expectancy%2C%20education%20and%20per%20capita%20income.%20In%202023%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.undp.org%2Findia%2Fpress-releases%2Findia-ranks-132-human-development-index-global-development-stalls%5C%22%3Ewas%20ranked%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20132.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Independence%2C%20Gujarat%20has%20always%20been%20under%20prohibition%20but%20had%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Findicators%2Fup-bihar-continue-to-be-down-in-the-dumps-in-hdi-report%2Farticleshow%2F68321457.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3EHDI%20rank%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%2014%20among%2025%20Indian%20states%20in%202017%20(%E2%80%9CHuman%20Development%20Index%20across%20Indian%20States%E2%80%9D%2C%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%20Issue%2094%2C%20FY%202019).%20Bihar%2C%20which%20is%20now%20under%20prohibition%2C%20ranked%2025%2C%20the%20very%20last%20among%20all%20states%20surveyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20Harvard%20Centre%20for%20Population%20and%20Development%20Studies%20assessed%20the%20performance%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20states%20and%20districts%20on%20the%20POSHAN%20Abhiyan.%20This%20was%20a%20programme%20launched%20in%20March%202018%20with%20a%20stated%20aim%20to%20achieve%20improvement%20in%20the%20nutritional%20status%20of%20pregnant%20women%2C%20adolescent%20girls%2C%20lactating%20mothers%2C%20and%20children%20under%20six.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fpolicy%2Ftwo-development-numbers-bust-growth-narrative%5C%22%3E%20Gujarat%20has%20the%20lowest%20rank%20at%2028.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20shows%20that%20it%20is%20very%20hard%20to%20relate%20prohibition%20in%20India%20to%20that%20constitutional%20goal%20of%20raising%20of%20the%20level%20of%20nutrition%20and%20the%20standard%20of%20living%20of%20its%20people%20and%20the%20improvement%20of%20public%20health.%20And%2C%20to%20be%20honest%2C%20this%20was%20never%20the%20real%20reason%20anyway%2C%20just%20as%20the%20desire%20to%20ban%20cow%20slaughter%20is%20unrelated%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cendeavour%20to%20organise%20agriculture%20and%20animal%20husbandry%20on%20modern%20and%20scientific%20lines%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20Article%2048%20puts%20it.%20It%20is%20just%20religious%20conservatism%2C%20parading%20as%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProhibition%20in%20India%20is%20pushed%20always%20from%20the%20moral%20point%2C%20that%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20well-being%20and%20societal%20well-being.%20The%20point%20made%20by%20Srinivas%2C%20that%20it%20represented%20a%20Sanskritic%20act%20that%20was%20linked%20to%20caste%2C%20is%20never%20raised%20in%20Indian%20debates%20and%20the%20disapproval%20of%20drink%20is%20almost%20universal.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706000451000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19170544%2Fimage-1075-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgujarat-lifts-its-alcohol-ban-for-some-a-sign-of-what-lies-ahead%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20a%20news%20report%20put%20it%2C%20this%20was%20done%20to%20'attract%20global%20financial%20institutions%2C'%20and%20to%20that%20end%20'alcohol%20would%20be%20allowed%20at%20hotels%2Frestaurants%2Fclubs%20offering%20%E2%80%98wine%20and%20dine%E2%80%99%20in%20Gujarat%20International%20Finance%20Tec-City%20(or%20GIFT%20City)%20near%20the%20state%20capital%20of%20Gandhinagar.%E2%80%99%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgujarat-lifts-its-alcohol-ban-for-some-a-sign-of-what-lies-ahead%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%3A%20At%20least%2020%20dead%2C%20dozens%20missing%20in%20Yunnan%20landslide%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706000427000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FE951%2Fproduction%2F_132392795_zhenxiong_county_getty.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-68065197%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Most%20of%20the%20city's%20residents%20were%20either%20elderly%20or%20children%2C%20one%20villager%20told%20a%20local%20news%20outlet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A42%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-68065197%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-68065197.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-68065197.amp%