%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20not%20everyone%20can%20buy%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApplicants%20must%20be%20under%2045%20years%20old%2C%20in%20a%20marital%20or%20extramarital%20partnership%2C%20have%20no%20criminal%20history%2C%20and%20can't%20already%20own%20property%20in%20the%20country.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Croatian%20government%20and%20local%20Legrad%20officials%20for%20further%20information%20on%20the%20stipulations%2C%20and%20if%20the%20program%20has%20changed%20since%20its%20introduction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20practically%20free%20homes%20are%20part%20of%20the%20small%20town's%20effort%20to%20increase%20its%20population%20of%202%2C000.%20The%20initiative%20first%20came%20over%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20it's%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bhouses%20for%20a%20penny%26quot%3B%20policy%2C%20local%20Croatian%20publication%20HRT%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmagazin.hrt.hr%2Fprice-iz-hrvatske%2Flegrad-opet-nudi-kuce-i-gradilista-za-13-centi--11285319%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20more%20children%20in%20Legrad%20since%20the%20policy%20went%20into%20effect%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20the%20municipality%20is%20building%20its%20first%20kindergarten%20as%20a%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20total%20of%20five%20houses%20ready%20for%20occupancy%20have%20been%20sold.%20Three%20families%20have%20already%20moved%20in%2C%20and%20what%20delights%20us%20is%20that%20all%20three%20families%20welcomed%20a%20new%20member%20during%20their%20move-in.%20This%20has%20increased%20the%20number%20of%20children%20in%20the%20daycare%20center%2C%26quot%3B%20Ivan%20Saboli%C4%87%2C%20the%20mayor%20of%20Legrad%2C%20told%20HRT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20available%20homes%20have%20varying%20levels%20of%20repair%20needs.%20When%2019%20houses%20were%20put%20up%20for%20sale%20in%202021%20for%20about%20%240.14%2C%20Legrad%20offered%20to%20pay%20%243%2C558%20for%20necessary%20renovations%2C%20Reuters%20%3Ca%20hre