%2Fmsid-107078440%2Cimgsize-52450.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Frohit-sharma-named-captain-as-icc-names-mens-odi-team-of-2023%2Farticleshow%2F107077932.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20has%20been%20named%20as%20the%20captain%20of%20ICC%20Men's%20ODI%20Team%20of%20the%20Year%202023%2C%20which%20includes%20Men%20in%20Blue%20stars%20like%20batting%20lynchpin%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20batter%20Shubman%20Gill%2C%20star%20pacers%20Mohammed%20Siraj%2C%20Mohammed%20Shami%20and%20spinner%20Kuldeep%20Yadav.%20The%20playing%20XI%20is%20also%20dominated%20by%20the%20Australian%20players%20who%20excelled%20during%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20which%20ended%20in%20their%20sixth%20title%20after%20a%20win%20over%20hosts%20India%20in%20the%20final.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Frohit-sharma-named-captain-as-icc-names-mens-odi-team-of-2023%2Farticleshow%2F107077932.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vicky-Ranbir-Katrina%20chat%20in%20Ayodhya%20video%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705999291000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107078316%2Cimgsize-23020.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvicky-kaushal-and-ranbir-kapoor-intently-listen-to-katrina-kaif-in-a-viral-video-from-the-ram-mandir-consecration-in-ayodhya%2Farticleshow%2F107078255.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107078255.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EFans%20are%20loving%20how%20Katrina%20Kaif%20and%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%20are%20mature%20and%20have%20moved%20on%20with%20their%20partners%20and%20continue%20to%20be%20comfortable%20and%20bonded%20with%20each%20other%20at%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20opening%20in%20Ayodhya%20as%20several%20videos%20go%20viral...%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ICC%20ODI%20Team%20Of%20Year%3A%20Rohit%20Named%20Captain%2C%20Kohli%20Among%206%20Indians%20Included%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERohit%20Sharma%20was%20on%20Tuesday%20named%20captain%20of%20the%20ICC%20ODI%20Team%20of%20the%20Year%2C%20which%20featured%20five%20other%20Indians%20including%20star%20batter%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20the%20pace%20duo%20of%20Mohammed%20Shami%20and%20Mohammed%20Siraj.%20The%20team%20mostly%20included%20the%20World%20Cup%20finalists%20--%20India%20(runner-up)%20and%20Australia%20(winner)%20--%20besides%20players%20from%20semi-finalists%20New%20Zealand%20and%20South%20Africa%2C%20the%20ICC%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20The%20top%20order%20includes%20openers%20Rohit%20and%20Shubman%20Gill.%20While%20the%20Indian%20captain%20accumulated%201%2C255%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2052%20last%20year%2C%20the%20latter%20struck%20a%20brilliant%20208%20against%20the%20Kiwis%20and%20also%20finished%20as%20the%20highest%20run-scorer%20(1%2C584)%20in%20the%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20number%20three%20was%20Travis%20Head%2C%20who%20was%20consistent%20throughout%20the%20year%20and%20performed%20exceptionally%20well%20during%20the%20global%20event%2C%20with%20his%20137%20in%20the%20final%20being%20the%20highlight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20middle%20order%20comprised%20Indian%20stalwart%20Kohli%2C%20followed%20by%20Daryl%20Mitchell%2C%20Heinrich%20Klaasen%20and%20Marco%20Jansen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%20finished%20as%20the%20second-highest%20run-scorer%20of%20the%20year%20in%20ODIs%20(1%2C337)%20and%20slammed%20six%20centuries%20during%20the%20year.%20He%20surpassed%20Sachin%20Tendulkar's%20record%20of%20most%20international%20tons%2C%20besid