e%20biggest%20operators%20of%20Boeing%20737%20Max%209%20jets%20and%20has%20had%20to%20cancel%20flights.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A39%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-68064948%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-68064948.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-68064948.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP-RSS's%20Structural%20Assault%20on%20Hinduism%20and%20the%20Advent%20of%20Hindu-Vatican%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F23130039%2FEffect-80.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EProgressive%20forces%20are%20legitimately%20concerned%20about%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janta%20Party%20(BJP)%20reshaping%20India%E2%80%99s%20political%20culture%20by%20deploying%20Hindutva%20(politicised%20Hinduism)%20and%20%3Cem%3ERashtrawaad%20%3C%2Fem%3E(nationalism)%2C%20which%20has%20profound%20constitutional%20and%20institutional%20implications.%20Some%20have%20argued%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3Epran%20pratishtha%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0ceremony%20marks%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EHindu%20Rashtra%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E(or%20more%20precisely%20the%20ethno-nationalist%20state)%2C%20while%20others%20have%20argued%20that%20it%20marks%20the%20end%20of%20a%20process%20that%20began%20in%20the%201980s.%20Either%20way%2C%20it%20will%20undoubtedly%20need%20concerted%20and%20creative%20efforts%20to%20restore%20the%20primacy%20of%20the%20constitutional%20idea%20of%20India%20and%20to%20reclaim%20hearts%20and%20minds.%20But%20little%20attention%20is%20being%20paid%20to%20how%20the%20BJP%20is%20extending%20its%20%3Cem%3Eg%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Eleichshaltung%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20process%20by%20which%20the%20Nazi%20Party%20established%20total%20control%20of%20the%20State%20in%20Germany)%20to%20religious%20and%20spiritual%20institutions.%20This%20religious%20%3Cem%3Eg%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Eleichshaltung%3C%2Fem%3E%20will%20irrevocably%20restructure%20Hinduism%20and%20have%20a%20sweeping%20socio-cultural%20impact%20on%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirstly%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20leveraging%20the%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20to%20effect%20a%20fundamental%20restructuring%20of%20Hinduism.%20Currently%2C%20Hinduism%20has%20no%20ecclesiastical%20order%2C%20absolutist%20establishment%2C%20governing%20organisation%2C%20or%20binding%20holy%20book.%20It%20has%20many%20%3Cem%3Esampradayas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(traditions)%2C%20which%20consist%20of%20monastic%20orders%20of%20the%20Vaishnava%20or%20Shaiva%20traditions%2C%20which%20have%20their%20own%20%3Cem%3Eakharas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Eashrams%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Emutts%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Then%20there%20are%20countless%20temples%20and%20temple%20trusts%2C%20the%20most%20prominent%20being%20the%20%3Cem%3Echaar%20dhams%20%3C%2Fem%3E(four%20ancient%20pilgrimage%20sites)%20and%20the%2012%3Cem%3E%20jyotirlingas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(revered%20shrines%20dedicated%20to%20Bhagwan%20Shiva).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fayodhya-land-wealth-babri-masjid-ram-temple%5C%22%3EDharmic%20SEZ%20and%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20Renaissance%E2%80%99%3A%20Ram%20Rajya%20for%20the%20Rich%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20infiltrated%20and%20misused%20many%20of%20these%20to%20further%20their%20politico-ideological%20goals%2C%20is%20now%20projecting%20the%20Ayodhya%20Temple%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3ERashtriya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(national)%20Temple.%20In%20this%20imagining%2C%20%3Cem%3Eakharas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Eashrams%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Emutts%3C%2Fem%3E%20will%20be%20reduced%20to%20franchises%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindu-Vatican.%20In%20doing%20this%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20reduced%20the%20temple%20(indeed%20every%20temple)%20to%20a%20tourist%20site%E2%80%94New%20India%E2%80%99s%20Essel%20World%E2%80%94with%20all%20of%20India%20waiting%20in%20queue%20with%20tickets%20in%20hand.%20This%20is%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EDharmashatras%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewhich%20describe%20a%20temple%20as%20a%20%3Cem%3Edevalaya%2C%20devayatna%2C%20and%20devagriha%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%94essentially%20a%20structure%20for%20divinity.%20But%20equally%20problematic%20is%20that%20this%20will%20severely%20undermine%20the%20temporal%2C%20financial%2C%20and%20administrative%20powers%20of%20existing%20religious%20and%20spiritual%20organisations.%20It%20is%20abundantly%20clear%20that%20the%20BJP%20(which%20once%20promised%20the%20elevation%20of%20status%20for%20Hindu%20religious%20leaders)%20has%20reduced%20them%20to%20props%20in%20their%20larger%20religio-political%20agenda.%20Given%20this%2C%20it%20will%20be%20interesting%20to%20see%20how%20the%20%3Cem%3EShankaracharyas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EGorakhnath%20muth%3C%2Fem%3E%20(headed%20by%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adiyanath)%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ENirmohi%20akhara%2C%20Nirvani%20akhara%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20other%20smaller%20%3Cem%3Eashrams%3C%2Fem%3E%20(like%20the%20%3Cem%3EShri%20Ram%20Ashram%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Ramkot%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EChandrahari%20temple%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20Ram%20ki%20Pauri%2C%20etc.)%20will%20react%20to%20this%20structural%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20the%20immediate%20consequence%20of%20this%20restructuring%20will%20be%20that%20it%20will%20constrict%20the%20socio-cultural%20malleability%20of%20Hinduism%20and%20alter%20the%20way%20it%20is%20practiced.%20Metaphysically%2C%20Hinduism%20was%20a%20synthesis%20of%20diverse%20spiritual%20and%20cultural%20traditions%20in%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent%20(that%20we%20popularly%20call%20India%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EGanga-Jamuni%20tehzeeb%3C%2Fem%3E).%20This%20has%20a%20normative%20basis%20that%20goes%20back%20to%20the%20Upanishad%20which%20says%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EAyam%20bandhurayam%20neti%20ganan%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%C4%81%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Elaghuchetas%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%C4%81m%2C%20Ud%C4%81%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Eracharit%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%C4%81n%C4%81m%20tu%20vasudhaiva%20kutumbakam%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(only%20a%20narrow-minded%20person%20calls%20one%20his%20brother%20and%20not%20the%20other.%20For%20those%20who%20are%20large%20hearted%2C%20the%20entire%20world%20is%20a%20one%20big%20family).%20Similarly%2C%20the%20Isha%20Upanishad%20(that%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20described%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fstream%2Fmkgpamphlet1800mkga%2Fmkgpamphlet1800mkga_djvu.txt%5C%22%3Ethe%20whole%20essence%20of%20Hinduism%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9C)%20said%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EIshavasyamid%20sarva%20yaktichh%20jagatya%20jagat%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(all%20that%20we%20see%20in%20this%20universe%20is%20pervaded%20by%20God).%20Similarly%2C%20numerous%20verses%20in%20the%20Rigveda%20(9%2F13%2F8%3B%206%2F47%2F13%3B%204%2F1%2F4%3B%202%2F6%2F4%20etc.)%2C%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3ESamveda%3C%2Fem%3E%20(134)%20go%20on%20to%20urge%20us%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdestroy%20all%20malicious%20inclinations%20of%20hatred%20and%20enmity%20towards%20anyone%E2%80%9D.%20The%20%3Cem%3EAtharveda%3C%2Fem%3E%20(17%2F1%2F7)%20goes%20even%20further%20to%20urge%20us%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccultivate%20love%2C%20affection%2C%20empathy%20and%20good%20will%20for%20all%20creatures%E2%80%9D%20(%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Eyanscha%20paschyami%20yanscha%20na%20teshu%20ma%20sumati%20krudhi%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22170459%2FGEb7QB7bMAA0uXA.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22170459%2FGEb7QB7bMAA0uXA.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22170459%2FGEb7QB7bMAA0uXA-300x185.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22170459%2FGEb7QB7bMAA0uXA-1024x630.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694009%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22738%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDevotees%20attending%20Ram%20Temple%20consecration%20ceremony%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2FBJP4India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20malleability%20and%20synthesis%20are%20why%20India%20always%20embraced%20multiple%20paths%20to%20%3Cem%3Enirvana%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20could%20be%20realised%20through%20a%20combination%20of%20%3Cem%3Ednyana%3C%2Fem%3E%20(knowledge)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebhakti%3C%2Fem%3E%20(devotion)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekarma%3C%2Fem%3E%20(action)%20and%20%3Cem%3Eyoga%3C%2Fem%3E%20(psychical%20control).%20Because%20of%20this%20plurality%20of%20paths%2C%20there%20have%20always%20been%20%3Cem%3Edevaghars%3C%2Fem%3E%20(home%20temples)%20and%20domestic%20rituals%20in%20every%20home%20(as%20detailed%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EGrihya%20Sutras%3C%2Fem%3E)%20which%20allowed%20for%20personal%20communion%20with%20the%20divine.%20This%20metaphysical%20diversity%20allowed%20people%20to%20be%20polytheistic%2C%20monistic%2C%20agnostic%2C%20pantheistic%2C%20monotheistic%2C%20atheistic%20or%20humanist.%20But%20all%20that%20will%20vanish%20when%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindu-Vatican%20reduces%20Hinduism%20to%20the%20performative%20and%20militant.%20Going%20forward%2C%20it%20is%20the%20BJP-controlled%20supreme%20body%20and%20pontiff%20that%20could%20well%20determine%20what%20it%20is%20to%20be%20a%20good%20and%20bad%20Hindu.%20Given%20what%20the%20far%20right%20in%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%E2%80%99s%20plethora%20of%20institutions%20have%20imposed%20onto%20India%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20it%20is%20very%20likely%20that%20rigid%20prescriptions%20will%20be%20imposed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Findiatoday.intoday.in%2Fstory%2Fbeef-ban-and-bloodshed%2F1%2F493111.html%5C%22%3Eon%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20clothing%20(women%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2F6-places-women-can-t-wear-jeans-or-leggings-in-india-248819.html%5C%22%3Ecan%E2%80%99t%20wear%20jeans%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2FNight-out-for-girls-not-in-our-culture-says-Union-culture-minister-Mahesh-Sharma%2Farticleshow%2F49019712.cms%5C%22%3Ego%20out%20at%20night%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20modes%20of%20societal%20conduct%20(pray%20only%20to%20this%20God%2C%20speak%20only%20in%20Hindi%2C%20marry%20only%20in%20this%20creed%20and%20caste%2C%20say%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fopinion%2Feditorial%2Fbharat-mata-ki-jai-debate-the-language-of-violence%2Farticle8442486.ece%5C%22%3EBharat%20Mata%20ki%20Jai%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThirdly%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20temple%20run%20in%20South%20India%20makes%20it%20abundantly%20clear%20that%20the%20BJP%20hopes%20to%20recreate%20what%20it%20did%2040%20years%20ago%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland.%20For%20its%20politico-ideological%20ends%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20again%20seduce%2C%20infiltrate%2C%20and%20misuse%20southern%20temple%20trusts%20(and%20their%20affiliated%20institutions)%20to%20breach%20the%20Great%20Wall%20of%20the%20Vindhyas.%20The%20southern%20temples%20which%20are%20laying%20out%20the%20red%20carpet%20for%20the%20BJP%20don%E2%80%99t%20realise%20that%20like%20the%20%3Cem%3EAkharas%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20North%2C%20they%20too%20will%20be%20used%20as%20a%20foothold%20for%20electoral%20benefits%20but%20eventually%20be%20cannibalised%20by%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20machinery.%20They%20need%20to%20just%20look%20at%20how%20the%20%3Cem%3EShankarcharyas%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EAkharas%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20being%20treated%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFourthly%2C%20this%20entire%20episode%20signals%20the%20capitulation%20of%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Although%20it%20plans%20to%20celebrate%20its%20centenary%20year%20in%20a%20grand%20way%20(2025%20is%20when%20the%20%3Cem%3ERashtriya%20Swayamsewak%20Sangh%3C%2Fem%3E%20turns%20100)%2C%20it%20will%20be%20an%20abject%20bystander%20to%20this%20commemoration.%20The%20RSS%2C%20which%20has%20never%20been%20a%20monolithic%20organisation%2C%20is%20currently%20undergoing%20a%20serious%20structural%20crisis%2C%20with%20its%20far-right%20and%20political%20wings%20colluding%20to%20programmatically%20actualise%20their%20core%20ideological%20projects.%20In%20doing%20this%2C%20they%20end%20up%20undermining%20the%20main%20organisation.%20Although%20the%20Sarsanghchalak%20and%20RSS%E2%80%99%20top%20leadership%20are%20trying%20hard%20to%20be%20relevant%2C%20many%20in%20its%20own%20top%20rung%20have%20surrendered%20their%20primacy%20and%20agency%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Going%20forward%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20hardline%20will%20drive%20the%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20social-cultural%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20this%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20hardline%20will%20keep%20the%20pot%20boiling%20by%20aggressively%20spearheading%20the%20demolition%20of%20mosques%20in%20Mathura-Varanasi%2C%20pushing%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act-National%20Register%20for%20Citizens%2C%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20One%20Nation-One%20Election%2C%20Akhand%20Bharat%2C%20etc.%20It%20is%20these%20pinpricks%20on%20the%20body-polity%20that%20will%20herald%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%20Rashtra%20%3C%2Fem%3E(rather%20than%20a%20formal%20declaration).%20This%20is%20a%20watershed%20moment%20for%20India.%20The%20%3Cem%3Ep%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Eanchajanya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(the%20conch%20that%20Lord%20Krishna%20blew%20to%20announce%20the%20Kurukshetra%20war)%20for%20the%20battle%20for%20both%20Hinduism%E2%80%99s%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20souls%20has%20been%20blown.%20The%20only%20question%20before%20us%20is%20whether%20we%20will%20fight%20this%20battle%20where%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20fought%2C%20and%20with%20the%20strategic%20and%20tactical%20prowess%20needed%20to%20breach%20this%20%3Cem%3Echakravyuha%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewe%20find%20ourselves%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPushparaj%20Deshpande%20is%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Samruddha%20Bharat%20Foundation%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705997100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F23130039%2FEffect-80.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Freading-into-bjp-rsss-structural-assault-on-hinduism-and-the-advent-of-hindu-vatican%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20has%20successfully%20leveraged%20Ram%20Mandir%20to%20effect%20a%20fundamental%20restructuring%20of%20Hinduism%2C%20which%20has%20no%20ecclesiastical%20order%2C%20absolutist%20establishment%2C%20governing%20organisation%2C%20or%20binding%20holy%20book.%20All%20of%20this%20could%20change.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Freading-into-bjp-rsss-structural-assault-on-hinduism-and-the-advent-of-hindu-vatican%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%20Texts%20Her%20Boss%20Claiming%20To%20Be%20Sick%2C%20Then%20Finds%20Him%20On%20Same%20Flight%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20Australian%20woman%20experienced%20the%20ultimate%20fear%20of%20every%20employed%20individual%20as%20she%20took%20a%20flight%20after%20reporting%20in%20sick%20to%20work%2C%20only%20to%20discover%20her%20supervisor%20on%20the%20same%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeila%20Soares%20posted%20a%20TikTok%20video%20capturing%20her%20predicament%20upon%20spotting%20her%20manager%20during%20her%20flight.%20The%20video%20gained%20immense%20online%20popularity%2C%20accumulating%20over%2011%20million%20views%20on%20TikTok.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20Mr%20Soares%20disclosed%20that%20she%20had%20called%20in%20sick%20to%20work%2C%20fabricating%20a%20health-related%20excuse%20for%20the%20day%20off.%20However%2C%20h