ch%20idol%20is%20special%20black%20granite%20brought%20all%20the%20way%20from%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20stone%20is%202.5%20billion%20years%20old%2C%26quot%3B%20confirms%20HS%20Venkatesh%2C%20Director%20of%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Rock%20Mechanics%20(NIRM)%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20national%20facility%20that%20helped%20in%20testing%20the%20stone%20using%20physico-mechanical%20analysis.%20The%20NIRM%20is%20the%20nodal%20agency%20to%20test%20rocks%20for%20Indian%20dams%20and%20nuclear%20power%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Venkatesh%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20rock%20is%20highly%20durable%20and%20resistant%20to%20climatic%20variation%20and%20will%20sustain%20thousands%20of%20years%20in%20this%20subtropical%20zone%20with%20minimum%20maintenance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fkelml7so_idol_640x480_22_January_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20granitic%20rocks%20formed%20when%20molten%20lava%20cooled%20down%20after%20the%20earth%20was%20formed.%20The%20granite%20is%20a%20very%20hard%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ram%20Temple%20has%20been%20constructed%20using%20traditional%20architectural%20designs%20and%20highest%20quality%20stones%2C%20yet%20it%20incorporates%20modern%20science%20and%20engineering%20techniques%20to%20make%20it%20durable%2C%20says%20Union%20Science%20Minister%20Jitendra%20Singh.%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20designed%20to%20last%20for%20more%20than%201%2C000%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stone%20was%20chosen%20from%20the%20village%20Jayapura%20Hobli%20in%20Mysuru%20district%2C%20a%20region%20known%20for%20high%20quality%20granite%20mines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rock%20is%20dated%20to%20the%20pre-Cambrian%20era%2C%20which%20is%20estimated%20to%20have%20begun%20some%20four%20billion%20plus%20years%20ago.%20The%20earth%20is%20estimated%20to%20have%20originated%20some%204.5%20billion%20years%20ago.%20The%20black%20granite%20rock%20from%20which%20the%20Ram%20Lalla%20statue%20has%20been%20sculpted%20has%20seen%20at%20least%20half%20or%20more%20of%20earth's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20humans%20appeared%20on%20earth%20about%2014%20million%20years%20ago%20and%20the%20humans%20as%20we%20see%20today%20-%20the%20species%20Homo%20sapiens%20-%20are%20only%20300%2C000%20years%20old.%20Scientists%20estimate%20that%20life%20originated%20on%20earth%20some%204%20billion%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fn1g2qg28_ram-lalla_625x300_22_January_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stone%20was%20carved%20into%20a%20beautiful%20idol%20by%2038-year-old%20Arun%20Yogiraj%20from%20Mysuru%2C%20who%20belongs%20to%20a%20family%20of%20five%20generations%20of%20sculptors.%20It%20took%20him%20about%20six%20months%20to%20craft%20the%20Ram%20Lala%20statue.%20Among%20his%20other%20well-known%20masterpieces%20is%20the%2030-feet%20black%20stone%20statue%20of%20Netaji%20Subhash%20Chandra%20Bose%20at%20India%20Gate%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NIRM%2C%20which%20helped%20assess%20the%20granite%20block%20with%20its%20testing%20laboratories%20at%20Kolar%20Gold%20Fields%2C%20told%20Nripendra%20Misra%2C%20chairperson%20of%20the%20temple%20construction%20committee%2C%20that%20the%20rock%20was%20%26quot%3Bmassive%2C%20melanocratic%20and%20uniform%20in%20colour%26quot%3B.%20The%20stone%20is%20fine-grained%2C%20hard%2C%20compact%20and%20has%20high%20compressive%20strength%2C%20tensile%20strength%2C%20bending%20strength%2C%20breaking%20strength%20and%20elasticity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rock's%20qualities%20make%20it%20amenable%20for%20any%20kind%20of%20carving%2C%20Dr%20Venkatesh%20says.%20%26quot%3BIn%20addition%20the%20rock%20possess%20high%20density%2C%20low%20porosity%20and%20water%20absorption%20with%20high%20P%20wave%20velocity%2C%20it%20is%20devoid%20of%20any%20internal%20cracks%20and%20fractures.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stone%20does%20not%20absorb%20water%20or%20react%20with%20carbon.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705996500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Flkgrubm8_ram-lalla_625x300_22_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fram-lalla-idol-at-ayodhya-carved-out-of-2-5-billion-year-old-black-granite-4915841%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20idol%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20or%20infant%20Lord%20Ram%20found%20a%20home%20on%20Monday%20with%20a%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20ceremony%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20at%20the%20new%20Ayodhya%20temple.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fram-lalla-idol-at-ayodhya-carved-out-of-2-5-billion-year-old-black-granite-4915841%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fram-lalla-idol-at-ayodhya-carved-out-of-2-5-billion-year-old-black-granite-4915841%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fram-lalla-idol-at-ayodhya-carved-out-of-2-5-billion-year-old-black-granite-4915841%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fintech%20firm%20Quinte%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20sign%20deal%20to%20set%20up%20development%20centres%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705996424000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2020-07%2F09%2Ffull%2F1594315734-4321.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ffintech-firm-quinte-tamil-nadu-sign-deal-to-set-up-development-centres-124012300334_