%20had%20a%20big%20cut%20on%20his%20head%2C%20and%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20blood.%20Only%20then%20did%20I%20begin%20to%20understand.%20I%20started%20screaming%2C%20calling%20Valerie%2C%20my%20wife.%20She%20was%20unresponsive%20and%20she%20seemed%20to%20have%20disappeared.%20I%20feared%20that%20she%20had%20been%20buried%20by%20the%20rubble%2C''%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2024%2F01%2F15%2Fnewlyweds-among-injured-floor-collapse-600-year-old-venue-20116774%2F%5C%22%3EMetro%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20six%20were%20left%20with%20serious%20injuries%20and%2010%20were%20%E2%80%98moderately'%20injured%2C%20with%20all%20of%20those%20hurt%20receiving%20treatment%20at%20the%20San%20Jacopo%20Hospital%20in%20Pistoia%2C%20Italy.%C2%A0Fortunately%2C%20all%20are%20in%20stable%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20images%C2%A0surfaced%20online%20showing%20the%20couple%20lying%20hand%20in%20hand%20beside%20each%20other%20in%20separate%20hospital%20beds%20with%20a%20drip%20attached%20to%20the%20groom's%20arm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20owners%20of%20the%20venue%20told%20a%20local%20newspaper%20that%20they%20didn't%20understand%20how%20the%20collapse%20happened%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Btragic%20and%20unpredictable%20event.%26quot%3B%C2%A0The%20former%20convent%20is%20now%20closed%20as%20police%20investigate%20its%20structural%20integrity.%20The%20couple%20have%20now%20filed%20a%20complaint%20against%20the%20venue%20with%20local%20prosecutors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705995720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F7v0v21bg_bride-and-groom_625x300_23_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnewlyweds-39-guests-fall-25-feet-as-dancefloor-collapses-during-wedding-in-italy-4915703%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20guests%20were%20dancing%20and%20enjoying%20themselves%2C%20a%20huge%20hole%20suddenly%20opened%20up%2C%20sending%20all%20of%20them%20plummeting%20through%20the%20floor.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnewlyweds-39-guests-fall-25-feet-as-dancefloor-collapses-during-wedding-in-italy-4915703%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnewlyweds-39-guests-fall-25-feet-as-dancefloor-collapses-during-wedding-in-italy-4915703%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnewlyweds-39-guests-fall-25-feet-as-dancefloor-collapses-during-wedding-in-italy-4915703%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Mamata%20Hints%20at%20Going%20it%20Alone%2C%20Bengal%20Braces%20for%20Likely%20Triangular%20Contest%20in%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKolkata%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20a%20likely%20setback%20for%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20block%2C%20West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20supremo%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20on%20Monday%20dropped%20clear%20hints%20of%20going%20it%20alone%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20addressing%20a%20Solidarity%20March%20criticising%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20inauguration%2C%20she%20indicated%20that%20her%20party%20was%20preparing%20to%20take%20on%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20on%20the%20one%20hand%20and%20a%20possible%20alliance%20between%20the%20Left%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Indian%20Secular%20Front%20(ISF)%20on%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20coined%20the%20name%20INDIA.%20I%20am%20sad%20to%20say%20whenever%20I%20attend%20the%20meetings%2C%20I%20see%20the%20CPI(M)%20is%20controlling%20the%20meetings.%20I%20fought%20them%20for%2034%20years.%20I%20will%20never%20take%20their%20advice.%20I%20felt%20insulted%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanerjee%20added%20that%20she%20had%20proposed%20that%20the%20Congress%20should%20let%20the%20regional%20parties%20deal%20with%20the%20elections%20in%20their%20strongholds.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20contest%20alone%20in%20300%20other%20seats.%20We%20will%20help.%20But%20they%20say%20they%20will%20do%20as%20they%20wish.%20Just%20keep%20one%20thing%20in%20mind%2C%20do%20not%20help%20the%20BJP.%20If%20you%20help%20the%20BJP%2C%20Allah%20%3Cem%3Ekasam%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20no%20one%20will%20forgive%20you.%20I%20will%20never%20forgive%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPI(M)-led%20Left%20Front%20governed%20West%20Bengal%20between%201977%20and%202011%2C%20until%20Banerjee%20toppled%20it%20in%202011.%20Her%20attack%20on%20the%20CPI(M)%2C%20nevertheless%2C%20is%20intriguing%20because%20the%20party%20reached%20a%20historic%20low%20between%202019%20and%202021.%20Even%20though%20the%20CPI(M)%20managed%20to%20slightly%20improve%20their%20vote%20share%20in%20the%202022-23%20civil%20and%20rural%20elections%2C%20they%20are%20not%20considered%20to%20be%20in%20a%20position%20to%20trouble%20the%20TMC%20electorally%20on%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20did%20not%20name%20the%20ISF%2C%20her%20reference%20to%20%E2%80%9Creligious%20leaders%E2%80%9D%20was%20understandably%20for%20Abbas%20Siddiqui%2C%20a%20cleric%20at%20the%20Islamic%20religious%20site%20Furfura%20Sharif%20who%20launched%20the%20ISF%20ahead%20of%20the%202021%20assembly%20election.%20Since%20then%2C%20Abbas%20has%20moved%20out%20of%20the%20limelight%2C%20and%20his%20brother%2C%20Nausad%20Siddiqui%2C%20is%20leading%20the%20ISF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENausad%20Siddiqui%20was%20the%20only%20candidate%20put%20up%20by%20the%20Left-Congress-ISF%20alliance%20to%20win%20in%20the%202021%20assembly%20election%20and%20has%20recently%20expressed%20his%20interest%20in%20contesting%20against%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20from%20the%20Diamond%20Harbour%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%20Abhishek%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20nephew%20and%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20all-India%20general%20secretary%2C%20is%20a%20two-time%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Diamond%20Harbour%2C%20where%20Muslims%20make%20up%20a%20sizeable%20chunk%20of%20the%20electorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20Monday%E2%80%99s%20event%2C%20the%20TMC%20supremo%20used%20most%20of%20her%20speech%20to%20win%20the%20confidence%20of%20Muslims%2C%20which%20indicated%20she%20is%20expecting%20to%20face%20the%20Left%2C%20Congress%20and%20ISF%20in%20alliance.%20While%20the%20Left%20and%20the%20Congress%20have%20a%20certain%20support%20base%20in%20the%20Muslim-majority%20districts%20of%20Murshidabad%2C%20Malda%20and%20Uttar%20Dinajpur%2C%20the%20ISF%20and%20the%20Left%20have%20some%20support%20in%20the%20Muslim-dominated%20pockets%20in%20the%20districts%20of%20North%2024-Parganas%2C%20South%2024-Parganas%2C%20Nadia%20and%20Howrah%20in%20south%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20they%20tried%20to%20bring%20NRC%20%5BNational%20Register%20of%20Citizens%5D%2C%20only%20we%20were%20on%20the%20streets%20and%20took%20out%20a%20unity%20rally.%20We%20protested%2C%20resisted%20and%20prevented%20the%20NRC%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20even%20on%20the%20question%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20inauguration%2C%20it%20was%20only%20her%20party%20that%20took%20to%20the%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22How%20Important%20are%20Social%20Media%20Influencers%20in%20Indian%20Elections%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhow-important-are-social-media-influencers-in-indian-elections%5C%22%3EHow%20Important%20are%20Social%20Media%20Influencers%20in%20Indian%20Elections%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20her%20speech%2C%20a%20senior%20leader%20of%20the%20Bengal%20Congress%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20state%20unit%20leaders%20were%20already%20in%20favour%20of%20allying%20with%20the%20Left%20but%20were%20waiting%20for%20the%20central%20leadership%20to%20decide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20that%20she%20has%20given%20her%20message%20clear%20and%20loud%2C%20we%20hope%20to%20get%20clearance%20from%20the%20top%20leadership%20to%20proceed%20with%20talks%20with%20the%20Left%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20leader%20said.%20The%20seat-sharing%20adjustment%20with%20the%20ISF%20would%20be%20taken%20care%20of%20by%20the%20Left%20parties%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECPI(M)%20state%20unit%20secretary%20Md%20Salim%20alleged%20that%20the%20TMC%20was%20trying%20to%20ditch%20the%20INDIA%20block%2C%20creating%20pretexts%2C%20but%20Banerjee%20would%20not%20succeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20has%20essentially%20been%20anti-CPI(M)%20since%20the%20mid-1980s.%20Even%20today%2C%20when%20the%20battle%20lines%20are%20clearly%20drawn%2C%20she%20chose%20to%20target%20the%20CPI(M).%20The%20whole%20argument%20behind%20creating%20the%20INDIA%20block%20was%20to%20build%20political%20momentum%20but%20she%20was%20interested%20only%20in%20seat%20sharing%2C%20not%20only%20in%20Bengal%20but%20also%20in%20some%20other%20states.%20She%20was%20never%20concerned%20about%20the%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20Salim%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20they%20have%20always%20favoured%20an%20electoral%20understanding%20with%20non-BJP%20and%20non-TMC%20forces%2C%20and%20are%20ready%20to%20negotiate%20not%20only%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20ISF%20but%20also%20any%20other%20Left%20party%20that%20would%20be%20ready%20to%20fight%20both%20the%20TMC%20and%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20Left-Congress%20seat-sharing%20talks%20broke%20down%20at%20the%20last%20moment%2C%20giving%20the%20BJP%20an%20edge%20over%20them%20in%20emerging%20as%20the%20main%20anti-TMC%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20anti-TMC%20votes%20consolidated%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20it%20recorded%20a%20meteoric%20rise%2C%20bagging%2018%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%2042%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20The%20Congress%20managed%20to%20win%20two%2C%20while%20the%20Left%20won%20none.%20The%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20tally%20came%20down%20from%2034%20in%202014%20to%2022%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20there%20is%20a%20view%20among%20a%20section%20of%20TMC%20leaders%20that%20while%20a%20triangular%20contest%20may%20give%20the%20BJP%20some%20chances%20in%20a%20few%20seats%20in%20the%20Muslim-majority%20districts%20if%20the%20anti-BJP%20votes%20split%2C%20a%20Left-Congress%20alliance%20can%20prevent%20consolidation%20of%20anti-TMC%20votes%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20favour%20in%20several%20south%20Bengal%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20precisely%20why%20the%20party%20chief%20seemed%20to%20be%20focused%20on%20winning%20over%20the%20confidence%20of%20the%20Muslims%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20veteran%20TMC%20parliamentarian%20unwilling%20to%20be%20named.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Left%20and%20the%20Congress%20are%20slated%20to%20face%20each%20other%20in%20Kerala%2C%20which%20has%2020%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20The%20political%20understanding%20is%20that%20the%20Left-Congress%20bipolar%20alignment%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20nature%20has%20kept%20the%20BJP%20at%20bay.%20Therefore%2C%20even%20if%20the%20two%20parties%20join%20hands%20in%20Bengal%2C%20is%20it%20unsure%20if%20the%20top%20leaders%20of%20the%20two%20parties%20would%20share%20a%20dais%20anywhere%20in%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaders%20of%20West%20Bengal%20BJP%20hinted%20that%20they%20may%20take%20the%20Hindu%20polarisation%20campaign%20to%20higher%20pitches.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20TMC%20is%20clearly%20trying%20to%20ensure%20the%20Muslim%20votes%20remain%20polarised%20and%20the%20Hindu%20votes%20get%20divided.%20That%E2%80%99s%20their%20strategy.%20We%20have%20to%20ensure%20the%20highest%20possible%20polarisation%20of%20Hindu%20votes%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MP%20hoped%20the%20central%20investigating%20agencies%20would%20make%20more%20raids%20on%20TMC%20leaders%20in%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20months%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20few%20more%20arrests%2C%20which%20would%20effectively%20turn%20the%20election%20into%20a%20Centre%20vs%20state%20and%20BJP%20Vs%20TMC%20battle.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20make%20it%20clear%20to%20the%20people%20that%20only%20we%20can%20take%20on%20TMC%2C%20only%20we%20can%20harass%20and%20punish%20the%20TMC%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705995568000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fas-mamata-hints-at-going-it-alone-bengal-braces-for-likely-triangular-contest-in-2024%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20the%20Hindu%20polarisation%20campaign%20to%20higher%20pitches.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fas-mamata-hints-at-going-it-alone-bengal-braces-for-likely-triangular-contest-in-2024%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ranveer%20Singh%20praises%20Mayyank%20Taandon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705995374000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107075751%2Cimgsize-25398.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Franveer-singh-praises-mayyank-taandon-who-made-his-debut-with-indian-police-force%2Farticleshow%2F107075594.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107075594.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EMayyank%20Taandon%2C%20who%20made%20his%20debut%20in%20Rohit%20Shetty's%20OTT%20show%20%26quot%3BIndian%20Police%20Force%2C%26quot%3B%20received%20praise%20from%20Ranveer%20Singh.%20The%20actor%20called%20Mayyank%20the%20%26quot%3BBest%20Boy%26quot%3B%20and%20commended%20his%20%26quot%3BSmashing%20Debut%26quot%3B%20on%20Instagram.%20Mayyank%2C%20who%20played%20Zarar%20in%20the%20show%2C%20expressed%20gratitude%2C%20highlighting%20Ranveer%20as%20his%20elder%20brother%20and%20thanked%20him%20for%20believing%20in%20his%20work.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Franveer-singh-praises-mayyank-taandon-who-made-his-debut-with-indian-police-force%2Farticleshow%2F107075594.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Is%20'Golden%20Visa'%20Scheme%20For%20Super-Rich%20That%20Australia%20Has%20Scraped%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAustralia%20has%20terminated%20its%20%26quot%3Bgolden%20visa%26quot%3B%20program%2C%20which%20granted%20wealthy%20foreign%20investors%20the%20privilege%20of%20living%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20policy%20document%20released%20in%20December%202023%2C%20the%20government%20announced%20the%20discontinuation%20of%20the%20golden%20visa%2C%20emphasising%20a%20shift%20towards%20creating%20more%20visas%20for%20skilled%20migrants%20capable%20of%20making%20substantial%20contributions%20to%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Australian%20government%20said%20that%20the%20program%20had%20not%20met%20its%20primary%20objectives%20and%20that%20it%20would%20instead%20focus%20on%20issuing%20more%20visas%20to%20skilled%20workers%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20obvious%20for%20years%20that%20this%20visa%20is%20not%20delivering%20what%20our%20country%20and%20economy%20needs%2C%26quot%3B%20Australian%20Minister%20for%20Home%20Affairs%20Clare%20O'Neil%20said%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20designed%20to%20attract%20foreign%20business%2C%20the%20golden%20visa%20scheme%20faced%20criticism%20over%20allegations%20that%20it%20was%20being%20exploited%20by%20corrupt%20officials%20for%20parking%20illicit%20funds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20its%20inception%20in%202012%2C%20thousands%20of%20significant%20investor%20visas%20(SIV)%20have%20been%20issued%2C%20with%2085%25%20of%20successful%20applicants%20hailing%20from%20China%2C%20according%20to%20government%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarketed%20as%20a%20means%20to%20drive%20foreign%20investment%20and%20stimulate%20innovation%2C%20candidates%20were%20required%20to%20invest%20over%20A%245%20million%20(%C2%A32.6%20million%3B%20%243.3%20million)%20in%20Australia%20to%20qualify.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClancy%20Moore%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Transparency%20International%20Australia%2C%20has%20applauded%20the%20decision%2C%20telling%20BBC%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20far%20too%20long%2C%20corrupt%20officials%20and%20kleptocrats%20have%20utilised%20golden%20visas%20to%20channel%20their%20illicit%20funds%20into%20Australia%2C%20potentially%20concealing%20the%20proceeds%20of%20their%20criminal%20activities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia's%20move%20follows%20the%20UK's%20decision%20to%20end%20its%20fast-track%20residency%20scheme%20for%20the%20mega-rich%20in%202022%2C%20citing%20concerns%20about%20the%20influx%20of%20illicit%20Russian%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20golden%20visa%20programs%20have%20faced%20scrutiny%20in%20Malta%20as%20well%2C%20where%20speedy%20citizenship%20is%20granted%20to%20wealthy%20non-European%20Union%20nationals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20an%20investigation%20revealed%20visas%20being%20granted%20after%20just%20a%20few%20days%20in%20the%20country%2C%20leading%20the%20EU%20to%20express%20concerns%20over%20potential%20risks%20of%20money%20laundering%2C%20tax%20evasion%2C%20and%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705995300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-07%2Ft8d2vrek_australia-generic-sydney-generic-sydney-opera-house-pixabay_625x300_29_July_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-is-golden-visa-scheme-for-super-rich-that-au