%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-man-fatally-shoots-wife-and-3-adult-daughters-inside-chicago-home-4915387%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-man-fatally-shoots-wife-and-3-adult-daughters-inside-chicago-home-4915387%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-man-fatally-shoots-wife-and-3-adult-daughters-inside-chicago-home-4915387%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Can%20Ram%20Temple%20Take%20BJP%20To%20400-Plus%20And%2050%25%20Vote%20Share%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20country%20is%20Ram-may%20(%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AE%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%AF)%2C%20with%20the%20Ram%20temple%20consecration%20ceremony%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20The%2051-inch%20idol%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%2C%20adorned%20with%20gold%20and%20flowers%2C%20was%20revealed%20shortly%20before%20the%20'Pran%20Pratistha'%20ceremony%20at%20the%20Ayodhya%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20supporters%20and%20strategists%20feel%20the%20fulfilment%20of%20the%20long-term%20promise%20will%20galvanize%20voters%20across%20the%20length%20and%20breadth%20of%20the%20country%20and%20propel%20it%20to%20400-plus%20seats%20and%20a%2050%25%20vote%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20Is%20Pan%20India%2C%20Contrary%20to%20Belief%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%2050%25%20vote%20share%20and%20400-plus%20target%20is%20bold%20-%20no%20party%20in%20India%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%20in%20its%20heyday%2C%20has%20breached%20this%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20once%20in%201984%20did%20the%20Congress%20cross%20400%2C%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20assassination%20and%20the%20consequent%20sympathy%20wave.%20Congress%20scored%20its%20personal%20best%20in%20the%20same%20election%20-%2048.1%25%20vote%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20political%20commentators%2C%20analysts%20and%20even%20some%20opposition%20parties%20still%20consider%20the%20BJP%20a%20north%20India%20party.%20That%20is%20far%20from%20the%20truth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20top%20eight%20states%20that%20account%20for%20223%20of%20its%20303-seat%20tally%20in%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20only%20three%20in%20the%20North%2C%20two%20from%20the%20East%2C%20two%20from%20the%20West%20and%20one%20from%20the%20South.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20states%20are%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(62)%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20(28)%2C%20Gujarat%20(26)%2C%20Karnataka%20(25)%2C%20Rajasthan%20(24)%20Maharashtra%20(23)%2C%20West%20Bengal%20(18)%20and%20Bihar%20(17).%20These%20states%20account%20for%20three%20fourth%20of%20the%20BJP's%20tally%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20also%20won%2014%20of%20the%2025%20seats%20in%20the%20northeast%2C%20excluding%20those%20won%20by%20its%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMission%20Impossible%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20won%20178%20of%20225%20seats%20in%20the%20Hindi%20belt%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20eastern%20states%20of%20Bihar%20and%20Jharkhand.%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20it%20won%2062%2F80%20seats%2C%20and%20faces%20a%20Samajwadi%20Party-BSP-Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20alliance%20that%20has%20weakened%20since%202019.%20The%20latest%20opinion%20poll%20of%20ETG%20suggests%20an%20increase%20of%20eight%20to%2012%20seats%20for%20the%20BJP%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bihar%2C%20due%20to%20the%20alliance%20with%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20United%20(JDU)%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20contested%20just%2017%20seats%2C%20winning%20all%20of%20them.%20As%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20party%20has%20left%20the%20alliance%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20likely%20to%20contest%20on%20more%20seats%20-%2030%20plus.%20The%20ETG%20poll%20suggests%20an%20increase%20of%20five%20to%20seven%20seats%20for%20the%20BJP%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20the%20Ram-maya%20environment%20does%20is%20that%20it%20neutralizes%20anti-incumbency%20against%20local%20MPs%20as%20well%20as%20against%20the%20central%20government%20due%20to%20unemployment%20and%20price%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20improves%20the%20probability%20of%20the%20BJP%20maintaining%20its%20seat%20tally%20in%20other%20states%20in%20the%20Hindi%20belt%20-%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20-%20provided%20it%20consolidates%20the%20Hindu%20support%20and%20manages%20a%20higher%20turnout%20amongst%20core%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20Bihar%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20likely%20to%20contest%20more%20seats%20in%20Punjab%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Maharashtra%20due%20to%20the%20exodus%20of%20allies.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20contested%20435%20seats%2C%20which%20may%20go%20up%20to%20475-500%20seats.%20This%20is%20likely%20to%20add%20votes%20and%20vote%20share%20to%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi's%20southern%20push%2C%20the%20BJP's%20alliance%20with%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20Secular%20(JDS)%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20local%20leadership%2C%20and%20the%20induction%20of%20Congress%20leaders%20could%20fetch%20the%20party%20a%20few%20additional%20seats%20in%20Telangana%2C%20Kerala%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20strategists%20hope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20can%20additional%20seats%20come%20from%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20was%20runner-up%20in%2072%20seats%20in%202019.%20The%20Congress%20won%20in%2015%20of%20these%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2021%2C%20BSP%2010%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%205%2C%20BJD%2011%20and%20others%20took%2010%20of%20these%20seats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%2072%20seats%20are%20located%20in%20Assam%20(1)%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20(2)%2C%20Goa%20(1)%2C%20Jharkhand%20(2)%2C%20Karnataka%20(2)%2C%20Manipur%20(1)%2C%20Kerala%20(1)%2C%20Maharashtra%20(2)%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20(1)%2C%20Odisha%20(11)%2C%20Punjab%20(1)%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20(5)%2C%20Telangana%20(2)%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(16)%2C%20Union%20Territories%20(2)%20and%20West%20Bengal%20(22).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2017%20of%20these%20seats%2C%20the%20BJP%20lost%20by%20a%20margin%20of%20less%20than%205%25.%20On%2015%20seats%2C%20the%20party%20lost%20by%20a%20margin%20of%20less%20than%2045%2C000%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20swing%20of%2010%25%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BJP%20on%2071%20of%20these%20seats%20(excluding%20Manipur)%20-%20meaning%20an%20increase%20of%205%25%20vote%20share%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20a%20parallel%20decline%20of%205%25%20in%20the%20winning%20party's%20vote%20share%20-%20could%20put%2038%20more%20seats%20in%20the%20BJP's%20kitty.%20This%20could%20push%20the%20ruling%20party's%20tally%2C%20theoretically%2C%20to%20341%20seats%2C%20assuming%20it%20is%20able%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20its%20303%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%2038%20additional%20seats%20are%20in%3A%20Assam%20(1)%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20(2)%2C%20Goa%20(1)%2C%20Jharkhand%20(2)%2C%20Kerala%20(1)%2C%20Maharashtra%20(1)%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20(1)%2C%20Odisha%20(6)%2C%20Telangana%20(1)%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(8)%2C%20Union%20Territories%20(2)%20and%20West%20Bengal%20(12).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gains%20could%20largely%20come%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(where%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20sans%20BSP%20is%20weaker%20than%20the%20SP-BSP-Congress%20alliance%20of%202019)%2C%20Odisha%20and%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Odisha%2C%20the%20BJP%20hopes%20voters%20backing%20Chief%20Minister%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20BJD%20in%20the%20state%20will%20vote%20Narendra%20Modi%20at%20the%20Centre.%20The%20BJD%20had%20won%2012%20seats%2C%20BJP%208%20and%20Congress%20one%20seat%20in%20Odisha%20in%202019.%20%C2%A0In%20three%20seats%2C%20the%20BJP%20lost%20by%20a%20whisker%20-%20less%20than%2035%2C000%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20West%20Bengal%2C%20the%20confusion%20over%20alliance%20seat-sharing%20between%20the%20Trinamool%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20high%20probability%20of%20Left%20parties%20staying%20out%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20and%20the%20elections%20being%20held%20in%20a%20highly%20polarized%20environment%20could%20help%20the%20party%20gain%20seats%20its%20strategists%20believe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20allies%20currently%20at%2030-odd%20seats%2C%20this%20could%20push%20the%20BJP%20to%20370-ish%20seats%2C%20in%20an%20optimistic%20scenario.%20The%20party%20needs%20to%20induct%20allies%20from%20the%20east%20and%20the%20south%20to%20breach%20the%20400-mark.%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20BJD%20and%20Jagan%20Reddy's%20YSRCP%2C%20who%20have%20adopted%20a%20pro-BJP%20stance%20in%20the%20past%2C%20could%20be%20candidates%20for%20joining%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20target%20appears%20to%20be%20improbable%2C%20but%20with%20a%20weakened%20opposition%2C%20and%20a%20positive%20environment%20created%20by%20inauguration%20of%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20it%20is%20not%20impossible.%20Politics%2C%20after%20all%2C%20is%20the%20art%20of%20impossible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705990020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F4i5t65jo_pm-modi-ram-temple_625x300_23_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcan-ram-temple-take-bjp-to-400-plus-and-50-percent-vote-share-4671818%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20target%20appears%20to%20be%20improbable%2C%20but%20with%20a%20weakened%20opposition%2C%20and%20a%20positive%20environment%20created%20by%20inauguration%20of%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20it%20is%20not%20impossible.%20Politics%2C%20after%20all%2C%20is%20the%20art%20of%20impossible.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcan-ram-temple-take-bjp-to-400-plus-and-50-percent-vote-share-467181