tent%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAustralia%20has%20decided%20to%20scrap%20a%20major%20visa%20program%20that%20provided%20overseas%20wealthy%20investors%20with%20the%20right%20to%20live%20in%20the%20country.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-68052626%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20scheme%20dubbed%20'golden%20visa'%20was%20halted%20after%20the%20Australian%20government%20found%20that%20the%20visa%20program%20was%20not%20delivering%20the%20desired%20economic%20outcomes.%C2%A0Introduced%20in%202012%2C%20the%20'golden%20visa'%20offered%20High%20Net%20Worth%20Individuals%20(HNIs)%20a%20way%20to%20gain%20permanent%20residency%20in%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''It%20has%20been%20obvious%20for%20years%20that%20this%20visa%20is%20not%20delivering%20what%20our%20country%20and%20economy%20needs%2C''%20Minister%20for%20Home%20Affairs%20Clare%20O'Neil%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20scrapping%20this%20programme%2C%20the%20Australian%20Government%20will%20be%20focusing%20on%20issuing%20more%20visas%20to%20skilled%20workers%20instead%2C%C2%A0capable%20''of%20making%20outsized%20contributions%20to%20Australia.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20Golden%20Visa%20scheme%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.com.au%2Fnational%2Fpolitics%2Fmajor-golden-ticket-is-quietly-scrapped-by-the-government%2Fnews-story%2Ff7d028fcd706e840d201a1d08528f2a8%5C%22%3ENews.com.au%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%C2%A0visa%20allowed%20foreign%20nationals%20to%20stay%20in%20Australia%20for%20up%20to%20five%20years%20if%20they%20invest%20at%20least%20%245m%20in%20approved%20investments.%C2%A0Of%20this%2C%20a%20maximum%20of%2060%20per%20cent%20can%20be%20invested%20in%20non-residential%20real%20estate%2C%20corporate%20bonds%2C%20and%20shares.%20The%20program%20was%20designed%20to%20attract%20more%20foreign%20businesses%20and%20investors%20into%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Home%20Affairs%20Department%2C%20more%20than%20100%2C000%20overseas%20migrants%20have%20used%20one%20of%20the%20BIIP%20streams%20to%20gain%20residency%20in%20Australia%20since%202012.%20Of%20these%2C%2085%20percent%20are%20Chinese%20millionaires.%20Unlike%20other%20visa%20schemes%2C%20the%20golden%20visa%20did%20not%20require%20people%20to%20speak%20English%20and%20did%20not%20have%20any%20age%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECriticism%20over%20the%C2%A0Golden%20Visa%20scheme%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20argued%20that%20the%20scheme%20only%20allowed%20wealthy%20foreign%20nationals%20to%20park%20illegal%20funds%20in%20Australia.%C2%A0A%20review%20in%202016%20showed%20that%20the%20policy%20had%20''potential%20for%20money%20laundering%20and%20other%20nefarious%20activities.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20inquiry%20by%20the%20Australian%20government%20also%20revealed%20that%20not%20only%20the%20'golden%20visa'%20programme%20was%20misused%2C%20but%20it%20also%20allowed%20people%20with%20'less%20business%20acumen'%20to%20reside%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClancy%20Moore%2C%20the%20chief%20executive%20of%20Transparency%20International%20Australia%2C%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E''For%20far%20too%20long%20corrupt%20officials%20and%20kleptocrats%20have%20used%20golden%20visas%20as%20a%20vehicle%20to%20park%20their%20illicit%20funds%20in%20Australia%20and%20arguably%20hide%20their%20proceeds%20of%20crime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilar%20investment%20visa%20schemes%20have%20been%20scrapped%20in%20Canada%2C%20Britain%2C%20and%20Singapore%20amid%20allegations%20that%20they%20have%20been%20abused%20by%20wealthy%20individuals%20and%20failed%20to%20benefit%20the%20countries%20themselves.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705989720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F202