0said%20that%20it%20was%20impossible%20to%20show%20respect%20to%20my%20religion%20standing%20on%20a%20pile%20of%20corpses.%20He%20felt%20obliged%20to%20pay%20respect%20to%20those%20who%20died.%20We%20declare%20them%20martyrs%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%20senior%20TMC%20leader%20later%20clarified%20that%20she%20was%20referring%20the%20the%20victims%20of%20riots%20following%20Babri%20masjid%E2%80%99s%20demolition%2C%20and%20not%20%3Cem%3Ekar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Esevaks%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Hindu%20nationalist%20volunteers)%20who%20died%20while%20attempting%20to%20pull%20down%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Maa%20Sita%E2%80%99s%20name%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20media%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EShe%20said%20she%20was%20not%20against%20Ram%20but%20respected%20both%20Ram%20and%20Sita%20and%20opposed%20the%20saffron%20camp%E2%80%99s%20rising%20of%20slogans%20only%20for%20Ram.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20ever%20raise%20Maa%20Sita%E2%80%99s%20name%3F%20Does%20it%20mean%20that%20you%20are%20anti-women%3F%20Ram%20is%20incomplete%20without%20Sita%20and%20Ram%20would%20not%20have%20been%20born%20without%20Kaushalya%20Devi.%20Sita%20spent%2014%20years%20in%20forests%20with%20Ram%20and%20then%20she%20had%20to%20give%20the%20Agni%20Pariksha%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Banerjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20started%20her%20Monday%20evening%20rally%20by%20paying%20visits%20to%20the%20Kali%20temple%20at%20Kalighat%20near%20her%20residence%2C%20and%20then%20a%20mosque%2C%20a%20gurdwara%20and%20a%20church.%20Representatives%20from%20different%20regions%20walked%20with%20her%20in%20the%20rally%20and%20were%20also%20on%20the%20dais.%20She%20named%20over%20a%20dozen%20Hindu%20pilgrimage%20sites%20and%20temples%20that%20her%20government%20has%20renovated%20and%20highlighted%20how%20she%20attends%20all%20religious%20festivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EShe%20also%20targeted%20the%20media%2C%20especially%20TV%20channels%2C%20for%20creating%20hype%20around%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20inauguration%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20the%20media%20owners%20and%20managers%20have%20been%20doing%20since%20the%20morning%20makes%20one%20wonder%20if%20the%20battle%20for%20independence%20was%20going%20on.%20You%20should%20be%20ashamed.%20Channels%20belonging%20to%20Adanis%20and%20Ambanis%2C%20only%20in%20their%20business%20interest%2C%20are%20selling%20people%20off%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20and%20even%20urged%20the%20people%20to%20boycott%20TV%20news%20channels.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20against%20reporters%20but%20I%20am%20ashamed%20of%20the%20media%20owners.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20even%20brought%20up%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20saffron%20camp%E2%80%99s%20promotion%20of%20vegetarianism%20through%20BJP-run%20governments.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20prohibiting%20the%20consumption%20of%20fish%2C%20meat%2C%20and%20eggs.%20I%20eat%20eggs.%20But%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20pregnant%20women%20to%20have%20eggs.%20They%20are%20deciding%20what%20people%20will%20eat%20or%20wear.%20I%20love%20vegetarian%20dishes%2C%20too.%20It%E2%80%99s%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20choice.%20Food%20is%20a%20personal%20and%20religious%20choice.%20We%20all%20eat%20fish%2C%20meat%2C%20and%20eggs.%20What%E2%80%99s%20the%20problem%20with%20it%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EShe%20ended%20the%20rally%20raising%20slogans%20of%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Hind%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Vande%20Mataram%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Joy%20Bangla%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20the%20last%20one%20more%20times%20than%20the%20others%2C%20indicating%20a%20possibility%20of%20her%20highlighting%20the%20Bengali%20ethnic%20plank%20during%20the%20coming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20294px)%2085vw%2C%20294px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F23103135%2Fsignal-2024-01-22-142608_003.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22294%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F23103135%2Fsignal-2024-01-22-142608_003.jpeg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F23103135%2Fsignal-2024-01-22-142608_003-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F23103135%2Fsignal-2024-01-22-142608_003-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694082%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22392%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAn%20activists%E2%80%99%20rally%20in%20Kolkata%20on%20January%2022.%20Photo%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EShe%20also%20dropped%20hints%20of%20leaving%20the%20INDIA%20block%20%E2%80%93%20or%20at%20least%20fighting%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20on%20its%20own%20%E2%80%93%20when%20she%20accused%20the%20CPI(M)%20of%20controlling%20the%20proceedings%20at%20the%20INDIA%20meets%20and%20the%20Congress%20of%20not%20heeding%20her%20proposal%20of%20letting%20regional%20parties%20take%20on%20the%20BJP%20at%20their%20strongholds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EJadavpur%20University%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20separate%20incident%2C%20a%20scuffle%20broke%20out%20at%20the%20Jadavpur%20University%20campus%20in%20the%20afternoon%20when%20supporters%20of%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%20(ABVP)%2C%20the%20student%20wing%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20parent%20body%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%2C%20tried%20to%20livestream%20the%20temple%20consecration%20event%20on%20the%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%20rally%20of%20students%20associated%20with%20leftist%20organisations%20allegedly%20heckled%20them%20and%20disallowed%20the%20event%2C%20ABVP%20organisers%20alleged.%20The%20Leftist%20students%20had%20called%20for%20a%20separate%20procession%20on%20the%20campus%20condemning%20the%20temple%20inauguration%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAnother%20rally%20protesting%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20inauguration%20event%20was%20taken%20out%20in%20the%20afternoon%20in%20Kolkata%20by%20various%20activists%20and%20organisations%20not%20associated%20with%20the%20TMC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20CPI(M)%20and%20other%20Left%20parties%2C%20too%2C%20took%20out%20protest%20rallies%20in%20different%20districts%20at%20the%20time%20the%20Ram%20temple%20inauguration%20was%20taking%20place.%20They%20have%20a%20scheduled%20rally%20in%20Kolkata%20on%20Tuesday%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20%E2%80%98Netaji%E2%80%99%20Subhas%20Chandra%20Basu%E2%80%99s%20birth%20anniversary.%20Left%20parties%20are%20also%20scheduled%20to%20hold%20events%20on%20January%2026%20in%20which%20the%20preamble%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20will%20be%20read%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMeanwhile%2C%20RSS%20helmsman%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20is%20scheduled%20to%20address%20a%20rally%20in%20Barasat%2C%20a%20town%20about%2030%20km%20north%20of%20Kolkata.%20The%20event%20is%20to%20pay%20tribute%20to%20Bose%20but%20RSS%20organisers%20in%20the%20state%20expect%20Bhagwat%20to%20raise%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20and%20criticise%20people%20who%20opposed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705986705000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F23103935%2FGEcTc-gaEAASTuO.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fram-temple-mamata-banerjee-modi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20TMC%20chief%20claimed%20her's%20was%20the%20only%20party%20to%20hit%20the%20streets%20against%20NRC%20and%20also%20against%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20inauguration.%22%2C%22author%