%20response%20is%20often%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20mental%20health%20support%20that%20effectively%20blames%20the%20farmers%2C%20and%20thereby%20teaches%20them%20%E2%80%9Cself-reliance%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cself-respect%E2%80%9D.%20Or%20we%20see%20corporate%20social%20responsibility%20programmes%20(run%20by%20the%20same%20corporate%20giants%20like%20Monsanto%20that%20have%20led%20to%20the%20crisis)%20who%20stress%20upon%20the%20need%20to%20educate%20the%20farmers%20on%20how%20to%20embrace%20a%20%E2%80%9Cneoliberal%20entrepreneurial%20mentality%E2%80%9D.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705984821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F18175002%2FSorghum-plant-Characteristics-Importance-Distribution-and-Uses.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fmarathwada-1088-farmers-died-by-suicide-in-2023-65-more-than-2022%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Since%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20came%20to%20power%20in%20the%20Centre%20in%202014%2C%20an%20average%20of%2030%20farmers%20have%20died%20by%20suicide%20per%20day%20across%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fmarathwada-1088-farmers-died-by-suicide-in-2023-65-more-than-2022%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sofia%20Vergara%20says%20her%20marriage%20to%20Joe%20Manganiello%20ended%20because%20she's%20ready%20to%20be%20a%20grandmother%2C%20not%20an%20'old%20mom'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sof%C3%ADa%20Vergara%20attends%20the%20'Griselda'%20premiere%20at%20the%20Callao%20Cinema%20on%20January%2009%2C%202024%20in%20Madrid%2C%20Spain%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65af1c1ddcdb354a985a0f1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222665%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESofia%20Vergara%20revealed%20the%20reason%20her