cruise.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDavid%20Purcell%20was%20among%20the%20would-be%20passengers%20devastated%20by%20the%20trip's%20abrupt%20cancellation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%20Purcell%20and%2077%20others%20are%20asking%20the%20US%20government%20to%20investigate%20Miray%20Cruises%20for%20fraud.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20an%20as-told-to%20story%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20David%20Purcell%2C%2078%2C%20a%20retired%20attorney.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%20Purcell%20was%20among%20the%20dozens%20of%20people%20who%20signed%20up%20for%20a%20three-year%20cruise%20with%20Life%20at%20Sea%20%E2%80%94%20an%20around-the-world%20journey%20that%20was%20canceled%20two%20weeks%20before%20its%20departure.%20He%20and%2077%20other%20would-be%20passengers%20who%20have%20not%20received%20refunds%20are%20asking%20the%20US%20Attorney%20in%20Southern%20Florida%20to%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flife-at-sea-passengers-3-year-cruise-demand-criminal-probe-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eopen%20a%20criminal%20fraud%20investigation%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20into%20Miray%20Cruises%2C%20the%20parent%20company%20of%20Life%20at%20Sea.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20representative%20for%20Miray%20Cruises%20denied%20the%20passengers'%20fraud%20accusations%20and%20said%20they%20would%20refund%20the%20passengers%20by%20February%2015.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20always%20interested%20in%20the%20ocean%2C%20which%20is%20tough%20for%20a%20kid%20growing%20up%20in%20eastern%20Kansas.%20In%201968%20when%20I%20was%20graduating%20from%20college%2C%20I%20opted%20to%20go%20to%20the%20Navy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20when%20I%20was%20doing%20estate%20planning%2C%20I%20did%20some%20gigs%20on%20cruise%20ships%20giving%20seminars%2C%20but%20being%20a%20passive%20passenger%20on%20a%20ship%20had%20very%20little%20intrigue%20for%20me%20until%20an%20article%20popped%20up%20on%20my%20radar%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flife-at-sea-cruises-canceled-no-ship-miray-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELife%20at%20Sea%3C%2Fa%3E%20cruise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%2C%20Beth%2C%20had%20been%20diagnosed%20with%20pancreatic%20cancer%2C%20and%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20to%20do%20and%20a%20lot%20to%20love%20but%20not%20much%20to%20look%20forward%20to.%20I%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BGod%2C%20this%20cruise%20is%20really%20something%20I%20could%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202023%2C%20I%20put%20down%20500%20bucks%20on%20the%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20can't%20appreciate%20the%20attraction%20of%20this%20cruise%20without%20looking%20at%20the%20itinerary%20%E2%80%94%20all%20the%20places%20we%20were%20going%20to%20go%20to%2C%20everywhere%20from%20up%20in%20northern%20Norway%20and%20down%20to%20Antarctica%20and%20circling%20New%20Zealand%20and%20Australia%20and%20down%20one%20coast%20of%20South%20America%20and%20up%20the%20other%2C%20and%20all%20through%20Asia%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20Mediterranean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20social%20and%20cultural%20aspects%20of%20it%20were%20almost%20more%20powerful%20than%20the%20sightseeing%20and%20Kodak%20moments.%20It%20was%20going%20to%20be%20a%20small%20enough%20ship%20to%20really%20create%20a%20community.%20So%20I%20was%20really%20looking%20forward%20to%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeth%20died%20on%20May%2012%2C%202023%2C%20and%20it%20was%20really%20sad.%20I%20didn't%20have%20any%20plan%20B%20for%20my%20life.%20We'd%20been%20married%20for%20nearly%2052%20years.%20We%20had%20lived%20in%20the%20same%20house%20for%2048%20years.%20We%20had%20three%20daughters.%20But%20this%20trip%20gave%20me%20something%20to%20look%20forward%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20June%2C%20I%20went%20ahead%20and%20I%20picked%20a%20cabin%20on%20the%20ship%20and%20put%20money%20down%20for%2C%20I%20think%20it%20was%20up%20to%2040%25%20of%20the%20cruise%20fare%2C%20about%20%2455%2C000.%3Cem%3E%20%5BEditor's%20note%3A%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20Purcell's%20purchase.%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sold%20my%20house%20in%20a%20screwy%20real-estate%20market.%20I%20had%20a%20little%20sports%20car%20I%20sold.%20My%20wife's%20car%20I%20gave%20to%20my%20daughter.%20I%20took%20economic%20hits%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20from%20living%20in%20a%20nice%20house%20in%20the%20suburbs%20to%20shutting%20that%20life%20down.%20I%20was%20couch%20camping%20with%20some%20generous%20friends%20who%20let%20me%20use%20their%20spare%20bedroom%20and%20getting%20ready%20to%20get%20on%20board%20the%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20having%20questions%20about%20the%20cruise%20that%20went%20unanswered.%20But%20it%20wasn't%20so%20much%20as%20to%20demand%20money%20back%20because%2C%20at%20some%20point%2C%20the%20most%20you%20could%20get%20back%20was%20the%2010%25%20of%20the%20money%20you%20put%20down.%20And%20nobody%20wanted%20to%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20couple%20of%20days%20before%20Thanksgiving%2C%20I%20got%20the%20call%20that%20the%20cruise%20was%20officially%20called%20off%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20in%20Roat%C3%A1n%20in%20Honduras%20on%20a%2015-day%20dive%20trip%2C%20trying%20to%20get%20my%20dive%20skills%20back%20up%20before%20the%20cruise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20spent%20Thanksgiving%20night%20in%20the%20Miami%20Airport%20so%20I%20could%20fly%20back%20to%20start%20a%20new%20life%20here.%20And%20I've%20given%20up%20my%20dreams%20of%20scuba%20diving%20around%20the%20world%20for%20a%20while.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20are%20probably%20calling%20us%20stupid.%20Well%2C%20OK%2C%20maybe%20there%20was%20an%20element%20of%20stupidity%20in%20this%2C%20but%20we%20were%20really%20sucked%20into%20this%20with%20a%20very%20dreamy%2C%20cool%20itinerary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20haven't%20gotten%20any%20money%20back.%20We%20want%20to%20see%20some%20justice.%20People%20need%20their%20money%20back.%20Some%