0Ram%20temple%20here%20a%20day%20ago%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fdiaspora-groups-ram-temple-consecration-precedent%5C%22%3Eclearly%20a%20Narendra%20Modi%20show%20all%20the%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBarring%20one%20or%20two%20of%20them%2C%20prominent%20Bhartiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20leaders%20who%20spearheaded%20the%20temple%20movement%20over%20the%20years%20remained%20conspicuous%20by%20their%20absence%20at%20the%20four-hour%20glittering%20event%20that%20was%20the%20high%20point%20of%20this%20historic%20day%20in%20the%20ancient%20temple%20town%20that%20now%20stands%20transformed%20into%20a%20city%20reverberating%20with%20chants%20of%20%E2%80%9CJai%20Shree%20Ram%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20literally%20stole%20the%20show%20right%20from%20the%20time%20of%20his%20landing%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20where%2C%20apart%20from%20800-odd%20VVIP%20guests%2C%20lakhs%20of%20devotees%20had%20converged%20to%20get%20a%20glimpse%20of%20the%20new%20temple%20at%20the%20long-debated%20birthplace%20of%20the%20Hindu%20deity%20Ram.%20The%20site%20was%20given%20to%20the%20temple%20side%20following%20a%20verdict%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Epran%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Epratishtha%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20or%20consecration%20of%20the%20new%20idol%20of%20a%20five-year-old%20Ram%20was%20also%20performed%20by%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20as%20was%20clearly%20seen%20%E2%80%93%20along%20with%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsewak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat.%20Following%20certain%20controversies%20that%20arose%20over%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20religious%20incapacities%20to%20carry%20out%20such%20a%20%E2%80%98high%20profile%E2%80%99%20ritual%2C%20the%20temple%20trust%20had%20sought%20to%20give%20the%20impression%20that%20a%20total%20of%2015%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ejajmans%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20or%20persons%20authorised%20to%20perform%20the%20puja%20had%20been%20handpicked%20for%20the%20rituals.%20However%2C%20what%20was%20apparent%20was%20that%20those%2015%20jajmans%20were%20sidelined%20while%20Modi%20who%20was%20stated%20to%20be%20there%20only%20as%20a%20symbolic%20jajman%20actually%20carried%20out%20the%20prime%20share%20of%20rituals%20with%20Bhagwat%20in%20tow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20significant%20deviation%20from%20the%20past%2C%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20who%20is%20the%20prime%20minister%20%E2%80%93%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20role%20of%20the%20judiciary%20in%20paving%20the%20path%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20he%20did%20not%20talk%20about%20the%20defining%20role%20of%20BJP%20stalwarts%20like%20former%20deputy%20prime%20minister%20Lal%20Krishna%20Advani%2C%20or%20former%20BJP%20chief%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%2C%20or%20frontline%20activists%20like%20Vinay%20Katiyar%2C%20Mahant%20Dharam%20Das%20and%20others%20who%20are%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20kept%20away%20from%20the%20ceremony.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fayodhyas-class-of-1992-the-key-conspirators%5C%22%3EAyodhya%E2%80%99s%20Class%20of%201992%3A%20The%20Key%20Conspirators%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20Ram%20Janmbhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20Trust%2C%20entrusted%20with%20the%20task%20of%20issuing%20invitations%2C%20did%20extend%20a%20formal%20invite%20to%20both%20Advani%20and%20Joshi%2C%20both%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fram-temple-trust-asks-bjp-veterans-advani-joshi-to-skip-inauguration-ceremony%5C%22%3Ewere%20stated%20to%20have%20been%20advised%20by%20those%20very%20trust%20officials%20to%20avoid%20travelling%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20view%20of%20their%20old%20age%20and%20accompanying%20physical%20infirmities.%20What%20prevented%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20make%20necessary%20arrangements%20for%20their%20travel%20is%20a%20mystery.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20fact%20remains%20that%20Advani%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20the%20temple%20movement%20is%20unparalleled.%20It%20was%20his%20%E2%80%98Somnath%20to%20Ayodhya%E2%80%99%20Rath%20Yatra%20in%201990%20that%20gave%20a%20huge%20boost%20to%20the%20temple%20movement%2C%20particularly%20after%20the%20yatra%20was%20stopped%20by%20then%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%2C%20who%20also%20put%20Advani%20behind%20bars.%20Advani%20is%20also%20credited%20with%20saving%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20scalp%2C%20when%20the%20then%20prime%20minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20appeared%20likely%20to%20sack%20Modi%20as%20Gujarat%20chief%20minister%20on%20account%20of%20the%20infamous%20communal%20riots%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETop%20Bajrang%20Dal%20leader%20and%20former%20BJP%20MP%20Vinay%20Katiyar%2C%20who%20was%20also%20among%20the%20key%20accused%20in%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition%20case%2C%20and%20had%20played%20a%20very%20aggressive%20role%20in%20the%20temple%20movement%2C%20was%20known%20to%20be%20present%20in%20Ayodhya.%20Yet%2C%20he%20did%20not%20attend%20the%20ceremony%20simply%20because%20he%20did%20not%20get%20a%20formal%20invite.%20And%20the%20same%20was%20the%20case%20with%20Mahant%20Dharam%20Das%2C%20the%20chief%20priest%20of%20Ayodhya%E2%80%99s%20oldest%20temple%2C%20Hanuman%20Garhi%2C%20who%20also%20stood%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20temple%20campaign.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20hour-long%20address%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20sought%20to%20point%20out%20how%20the%20%E2%80%98pran%20pratishtha%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20new%20era.%20Terming%20the%20event%20a%20%E2%80%98defining%20moment%2C%E2%80%99%20he%20urged%20people%20not%20to%20take%20it%20as%20a%20moment%20of%20just%20victory%20but%20also%20one%20of%20%3Cem%3Evinay%3C%2Fem%3E%20(prayer%20or%20humility).%20He%20also%20expressed%20the%20need%20for%20people%20to%20imbibe%20the%20rich%20ideals%20of%20Ram%2C%20who%20believed%20in%20compassion%2C%20justice%20and%20peace.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20day%20marks%20the%20change%20of%20an%20era%20and%20today%E2%80%99s%20generations%20should%20feel%20blessed%20to%20be%20witness%20it%20today%3B%20we%20should%20feel%20privileged%20and%20understand%20that%20we%20must%20now%20lay%20the%20foundations%20for%20a%20thousand%20years%20ahead%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Modi%2C%20amidst%20cheers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Flk-advani-rath-yatra-communal-violence-agra-babri-masjid-demolition%5C%22%3ENight%20of%20Terror%3A%20The%20Dust%20Kicked%20up%20Before%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20Demolition%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20tell%20everyone%20that%20he%20was%20at%20the%20Ram%20Setu%20a%20day%20earlier.%20He%20also%20recalled%20how%20Ram%2C%20too%2C%20had%20begun%20his%20return%20journey%20from%20Lanka%20to%20Ayodhya%20from%20that%20very%20spot%2C%20after%20defeating%20Ravan.%20He%20also%20added%20that%20he%20was%20here%20not%20without%20observing%20an%2011-day%20fast%2C%20during%20which%20he%20offered%20prayers%20at%20select%20temples%20in%20the%20southern%20Indian%20states%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Karnataka%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20He%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20break%20that%20fast%20in%20full%20view%20of%20the%20cameras%20by%20accepting%20water%20from%20Govind%20Dev%20Giri%2C%20treasurer%20of%20the%20temple%20trust.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20show%20after%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20began%20with%20an%20address%20by%20Govind%20Dev%20Giri%20%2C%20who%20only%20sang%20paeans%20for%20Modi%2C%20before%20handing%20over%20the%20mic%20to%20Bhagwat%2C%20who%20als