20churches%20for%20Christians%20and%20mosques%20for%20Mohammedans.%E2%80%9D%20In%20his%20book%20%3Cem%3ELectures%20from%20Colombo%20to%20Almora%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3EVivekananda%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CNay%20more%2C%20to%20understand%20that%20not%20only%20should%20we%20be%20charitable%2C%20but%20also%20positively%20helpful%20to%20each%20other%2C%20however%20different%20our%20religious%20ideas%20and%20convictions%20may%20be.%20And%20that%20is%20exactly%20what%20we%20do%20in%20India%20as%20I%20have%20just%20related%20to%20you%E2%80%A6%20That%20is%20the%20thing%20to%20do.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20present%20atmosphere%20is%20in%20total%20contrast%20to%20this%20as%20reflected%20by%20the%20fast%20of%20Suranya.%20It%20is%20also%20reflected%20in%20the%20incidents%20where%20cultural%20activists%20screening%20censor%20board-approved%20all-time%20classic%20by%20Anand%20Patwardhan%2C%20%3Cem%3ERam%20Ke%20Naam%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20being%20arrested%20and%20issued%20non-bailable%20arrest%20warrants.%20This%20happened%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20January%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22170459%2FGEb7QB7bMAA0uXA.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22170459%2FGEb7QB7bMAA0uXA.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22170459%2FGEb7QB7bMAA0uXA-300x185.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22170459%2FGEb7QB7bMAA0uXA-1024x630.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694009%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22738%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDevotees%20attending%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20consecration%20ceremony%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2FBJP4India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20are%20claims%20by%20the%20likes%20of%20Prafulla%20Ketkar%2C%20editor%20of%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20mouthpiece%20%3Cem%3EOrganiser%3C%2Fem%3E%20claiming%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20%3Cem%3Epran-pratishta%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(consecration%20ceremony)%20of%C2%A0Ram%C2%A0Lalla%20in%20Ayodhya%20was%20not%20simply%20the%20culmination%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-congress-clearly-saying-january-22-is-part-of-rss-bjps-political-project-matters%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-congress-clearly-saying-january-22-is-part-of-rss-bjps-political-project-matters%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1706003019298000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3CIfYpSSe6mcvyNEv9ccU_%5C%22%3Eof%20the%20decades-old%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%2C%20but%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98reconstruction%20of%20national%20consciousness'%E2%80%9D.%20This%20essentially%20means%20the%20whole%20process%20of%20social%20change%20and%20the%20idea%20of%20India%20which%20accompanied%20the%20freedom%20movement%20is%20now%20negated%2C%20with%20the%20advent%20of%20what%20can%20roughly%20called%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20India%E2%80%99.%20Communal%20forces%20through%20multiple%20steps%20have%20achieved%20Hindu%20Rasthtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20accompanied%20the%20%E2%80%98idea%20of%20India%E2%80%99%20was%20a%20coming%20together%20of%20different%20sections%20of%20society%20to%20fight%20the%20colonial%20powers%2C%20striving%20to%20establish%20liberty%2C%20equality%2C%20fraternity%2C%20and%20justice%20for%20all.%20This%20massive%20movement%20had%20the%20overarching%20%E2%80%98idea%20of%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20culminated%20in%20the%20values%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-babri-masjid-demolition-went-unpunished-and-the-fight-for-justice-died%5C%22%3EAll%20You%20Need%20to%20Know%3A%20How%20The%20Babri%20Masjid%20Demolition%20Went%20Unpunished%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20challenges%20to%20this%20idea%20of%20India%2C%20which%20were%20rooted%20in%20the%20values%20of%20kingdoms%20and%20what%20can%20be%20roughly%20called%20feudal%20society.%20The%20core%20of%20these%20values%20which%20are%20being%20hailed%20by%20these%20forces%20creating%20hysteria%20around%20temple%20consecration%20were%2Fare%20the%20birth-based%20hierarchies%20of%20caste%2C%20class%2C%20and%20gender.%20The%20roots%20of%20these%20lay%20in%20the%20kings%20and%20landlords%20of%20different%20religions%20and%20their%20ideologues%20who%20came%20forward%20as%20Muslim%20League%2C%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%2C%20and%20RSS.%20While%20Muslim%20communal%20forces%20are%20implementing%20their%20idea%20of%20feudal%20values%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20the%20Hindu%20communal%20forces%20are%20now%20rejoicing%2C%20in%20gradually%20increasing%20intensity%2C%20now%20reaching%20its%20semi-peak%20with%20Ram%20Temple%20consecration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20India%20of%20the%20freedom%20movement%20got%20itself%20manifested%20in%20the%20values%20of%20Bhagat%20Singh%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20and%20Gandhi%20focusing%20on%20liberty%2C%20equality%2C%20and%20fraternity%20or%20friendship.%20Despite%20a%20few%20differences%20with%20the%20Father%20of%20the%20Nation%2C%20Subhash%20Chandra%20Bose%20was%20also%20firmly%20committed%20to%20this%20%E2%80%9Cidea%20of%20India%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20elite%20landlord%20and%20Manusmiriti%20worshipping%20ideology%20was%20the%20social%20base%20of%20Hindu%20Rashtra%2C%20Hindutva.%20These%20forces%20and%20this%20ideology%20have%20grown%20stronger%2C%20particularly%20during%20the%20last%20four%20decades%20and%20are%20rejoicing%20the%20sectarianism%20becoming%20stronger%20by%20the%20day.%20They%20are%20also%20giving%20narrow%20projection%20of%20the%20temple%20consecration%20in%20contrast%20to%20what%20Gandhi%20and%20Vivekananda%20stood%20for.%20The%20sectarian%20nationalists%20are%20for%20the%20further%20deepening%20of%20particular%20%E2%80%98civilisational%20values%E2%80%99%20inherent%20in%20what%20can%20be%20called%20as%20Brahmanism%20inherent%20in%20Manusmriti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20standing%20for%20doing%20away%20with%20the%20values%20of%20Manusmriti%2C%20those%20integrating%20all%20into%20the%20umbrella%20of%20Indian-ness%2C%20those%20who%20have%20stood%20together%20cutting%20across%20class%2C%20caste%2C%20and%20gender%20are%20currently%20under%20different%20types%20of%20intimidations%20of%20Hindu%20India%2C%20the%20parallel%20and%20opposite%20of%20Muslim%20Pakistan%20are%20emerging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20ray%20of%20hope%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98idea%20of%20India%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20same%20classes%20of%20society%20who%20ushered%20in%20the%20Idea%20of%20India%20during%20the%20freedom%20movement%20to%20come%20together.%20It%20is%20their%20collective%20movement%3B%20the%20overarching%20effort%20to%20undermine%20the%20forces%20which%20gloat%20over%20the%20birth-based%20hierarchical%20values%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion%2C%20those%20who%20uphold%20the%20Holy%20Scriptures%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20Indian%20constitution.%20Their%20movements%20have%20been%20scattered.%20Their%20group%20interests%20may%20be%20different%20but%20their%20interests%20in%20protecting%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20and%20Idea%20of%20India%20which%20emerged%20during%20freedom%20movements%20do%20need%20a%20collective%20expression%2C%20cutting%20across%20the%20groups-%20party%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20non-sectarian%20parties%20do%20exist%20today.%20The%20predecessors%20of%20many%20of%20these%20had%20fought%20the%20British%20colonial%20powers%20together%20despite%20their%20differences.%20It%20is%20time%20for%20the%20social%20and%20political%20alliance%20of%20these%20sections%20of%20society%20given%20primacy.%20As%20colonial%20rule%20was%20detrimental%20to%20the%20interests%20of%20large%20sections%20of%20society%2C%20similarly%20those%20in%20power%20ruling%20through%20polarisation%20are%20also%20out%20to%20undermine%20the%20rights%20of%20weaker%20sections%20of%20society.%20This%20is%20abundantly%20clear%20during%20the%20last%20ten%20years%20or%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHysteria%20cannot%20be%20combated%20by%20hysteria.%20We%20need%20the%20ideology%20which%20binds%20the%20weaker%20sections%20of%20society%3A%20Dalits%2C%20religious%20minorities%2C%20women%2C%20workers%2C%20and%20Adivasis.%20They%20have%20many%20common%20values%20to%20protect%20and%20that%20is%20the%20%E2%80%98Idea%20of%20India%E2%80%99%20which%20came%20with%20the%20freedom%20movement.%20Can%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20be%20the%20first%20step%20in%20building%20such%20a%20common%20platform%2C%20can%20the%20Yatra%20succeed%20in%20doing%20this%20is%20the%20question%20baying%20us%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705976954000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22170222%2FEffect-78.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fto-combat-hysteria-around-ram-mandir-an-inclusive-idea-of-india-must-be-reinforced%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20'idea%20of%20India'%2C%20which%20stands%20for%20equality%2C%20liberty%2C%20and%20fraternity%2C%20is%20under%20threat%20today.%20It%20is%20time%20for%20political%20forces%20which%20support%20such%20idea%20of%20India%20must%20bring%20together%20Dalits%2C%20Adivasis%2C%20minorities%2C%20and%20women%20to%20safeguard%20this%20nation%20from%20the%20onslaught%20of%20communal%20forces.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fto-combat-hysteria-around-ram-mandir-an-inclusive-idea-of-india-must-be-reinforced%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lonely%20giraffe%20emba