20eldest%20daughter%20on%20vacation%20at%20a%20hotel%20in%20Sydney.%3Cp%3ETatyana%20Leonov%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETatyana%20Leonov%20and%20her%20eldest%20daughter%20take%20a%20trip%20alone%20together%20once%20a%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThree%20years%20ago%2C%20her%20younger%20child%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20Angelman%20syndrome%2C%20a%20rare%20neurogenetic%20condition.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20trips%20have%20helped%20strengthen%20the%20whole%20family's%20bond.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20hadn't%20even%20checked%20in%20yet%2C%20and%20my%204-year-old%20daughter's%20hands%20were%20full%20of%20sweets.%20It%20took%20her%20less%20than%20a%20minute%20to%20discover%20the%20help-yourself%20candy%20bar%20near%20the%20check-in%20counter%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-friendly-trips-asia-australia-tips-where-to-go-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESydney's%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ovolo%20Woolloommooloo%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20first%20time%20my%20oldest%20daughter%20and%20I%20had%20traveled%20together%20as%20a%20duo%20since%20the%20birth%20of%20my%20second%20child.%20That%20trip%20was%20almost%20three%20years%20ago%20now%2C%20and%20we've%20made%20it%20a%20tradition.%20Although%20it's%20tough%20to%20say%20goodbye%20to%20my%20husband%20and%20baby%20girl%2C%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fone-on-one-time-children-mother-daughter-relationship-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone-on-one%20time%20has%20become%20essential%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20ago%2C%20at%208%20months%20old%2C%20our%20youngest%20child%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20a%20rare%20neurogenetic%20condition%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcureangelman.org.au%2Fwhat-is-angelman%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAngelman%20syndrome%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20complex%20disorder%20primarily%20affects%20the%20nervous%20system%20and%20causes%20significant%20delays%20in%20almost%20all%20aspects%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20turned%20our%20lives%20upside%20down%20and%20most%20days%20now%20are%20a%20challenge.%20We%20find%20ourselves%20very%20time-constrained%20as%20she%20attends%20multiple%20therapies%20every%20week%20and%20deals%20with%20complex%20medical%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20live%20in%20suburban%20Sydney%2C%20and%20with%20so%20many%20therapies%20and%20appointments%2C%20I%20spend%20long%20chunks%20of%20the%20day%20in%20the%20car%20getting%20our%20little%20one%20from%20A%20to%20B%20(and%20often%20C%2C%20D%2C%20E%2C%20and%20F).%20Thankfully%2C%20we%20have%20supportive%20family%20members%20and%20friends%20who%20help%20from%20time%20to%20time%20with%20shuttling%20my%20eldest%20to%20her%20many%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENew%20dreams%20and%20new%20plans%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Young%20girl%20dancing%20with%20clowns%20and%20amusement%20park%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ae0e5e617029e90a5ee06f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20eldest%20daughter's%20first%20%26quot%3BYes%20Day%26quot%3B%20at%20a%20theme%20park%20in%20Sydney.%3Cp%3ETatyana%20Leonov%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20our%20original%20dreams%20have%20been%20shattered%20(most%20people%20with%20Angelman%20syndrome%20require%20lifelong%20care%2C%20and%20are%20not%20able%20to%20do%20things%20like%20go%20camping%20with%20friends%2C%20get%20a%20job%2C%20or%20find%20a%20partner)%2C%20we've%20crafted%20new%20ones%20and%20continue%20to%20strive%20for%20the%20things%20we%20imagined%20we%20would%20do%20as%20a%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20of%20us%20still%20manage%20to%20travel%20together%20and%20visit%20the%20same%20locations%20as%20before%20D-Day%20%E2%80%94%20a%20nickname%20used%20within%20the%20special%20needs%20community%20for%20Diagnosis%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%2