e%20such%20that%20they%20raise%20their%20flag%20by%20insulting%20other%20religions.%20The%20way%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20name%20is%20being%20used%20to%20spread%20this%20frenzy%2C%20the%20fire%20will%20tomorrow%20also%20engulf%20the%20homes%20of%20those%20who%20sow%20the%20seeds%20of%20this%20crop%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tiwari%20said%20in%20a%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20contacted%20a%20police%20officer%20from%20the%20Ranapur%20police%20station%20and%20dialed%20the%20CUG%20(closed%20user%20group)%20numbers%20of%20the%20station%20officer%20of%20Ranapur%20police%20station%20and%20the%20additional%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20in%20Jhabua%2C%20but%20could%20not%20reach%20them%20for%20immediate%20comment.%20The%20story%20will%20be%20updated%20as%20and%20when%20more%20information%20is%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705931467000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22190551%2Fimage-1782.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmp-right-wing-activists-plant-saffron-flag-on-the-holy-cross-on-the-eve-of-ram-temple-ceremony%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20was%20one%20of%20the%20four%20incidents%20that%20took%20place%20on%20January%2021%20in%20the%20Jhabua%20district.%20Saffron%20flags%20were%20placed%20on%20'churches'%20in%20four%20villages%20within%20the%20district%2C%20mainly%20dominated%20by%20tribals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A104%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmp-right-wing-activists-plant-saffron-flag-on-the-holy-cross-on-the-eve-of-ram-temple-ceremony%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Houthi%20social%20media%20sensation%20compared%20to%20Hollywood%20stars%20calls%20on%20UK%20and%20US%20to%20'stop%20this%20war'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705929060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F768x432%2Fskynews-rashid-al-hadd