e%20state%20of%20alertness.%20During%20the%20quest%2C%20he%20would%20also%20fully%20utilise%20Bombay%20Police%E2%80%99s%20Fingerprint%20Bureau%20and%20the%20Police%20Dog%20Squad.%20He%20placed%20informers%20in%20almost%20all%20the%20colonies%20in%20the%20then%20Bombay%2C%20He%20would%20only%20rest%20once%20he%20had%20enough%20evidence%20against%20the%20accused%20so%20that%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20get%20away%20in%20the%20court%20for%20the%20lack%20of%20it.%20However%2C%20he%20was%20against%20the%20practice%20of%20third-degree%20torture%20of%20criminals%20as%20he%20found%20it%20quite%20inhuman%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20book%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20his%20career%2C%20he%20solved%20many%20high-profile%20cases%20including%20the%20Turf%20Soda%20Factory%20murder%20case%2C%20the%20then%20Bombay%E2%80%99s%20Central%20Bank%20robbery%2C%20Lloyd%20Bank%20robbery%20case%2C%20Kuldeep%20murder%20case%2C%20and%20the%20Bombay%20House%20robbery%20case%2C%20amongst%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20would%20find%20clues%20from%20the%20most%20unexpected%20sources%20like%20in%20the%20Bombay%20Lloyds%20Bank%20robbery%20case%2C%20which%20he%20solved%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20clue%20given%20by%20a%20schoolgirl%20or%20an%20unclaimed%20car%20parked%20on%20Mohammad%20Ali%20Road%20in%20the%20then%20Bombay%E2%80%99s%20Central%20Bank%20robbery%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20truly%20a%20Sherlock%20Holmes%20of%20his%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EImages%20courtesy%20Mumbai%20Police%3A%20Urbs%20Prima%20in%20Indis%20(Photos%20of%20the%20officers)%2C%20Dhaval%20Kulkarni%20(Photos%20of%20the%20building)%20and%20Deepak%20Rao%20(Photos%20of%20the%20fingerprints%2C%20the%20Chunawala%20family%20and%20the%20two%20accused)%20and%20The%20Queen%20of%20Indian%20Pop%3A%20The%20Authorised%20Biography%20of%20Usha%20Uthup%20by%20Vikas%20Jha%20(Photo%20of%20Vaidyanath%20Someshwar%20Sami%20in%20a%20police%20uni